`,c(`// vs "Bun runtime" → ~3k`)]})},{icon:`⚐`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`--strip-types 让 TS 不需要 build`}),desc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`22 起实验支持直接 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`node --experimental-strip-types src/index.ts`}),`, 把类型注释当注释跳过。dev 不再需要 tsx / ts-node。`]})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`--strip-types removes the build step`}),desc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`22 ships experimental `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`node --experimental-strip-types src/index.ts`}),` — type annotations are stripped at load time. No more tsx / ts-node for dev.`]})},code:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`$ `,o(`node`),` --experimental-strip-types src/index.ts`]})}],adopters:[{name:`Vercel · Next.js`,href:`https://nextjs.org`,highlight:!0,zhNote:`dev / build / SSR runtime 都是 Node`,enNote:`dev / build / SSR runtime all Node`},{name:`Vite · Rolldown · esbuild`,href:`https://vitejs.dev`,highlight:!0,zhNote:`前端工程链顶梁, 全部跑在 Node`,enNote:`Frontend toolchain backbone, all on Node`},{name:`Electron`,href:`https://electronjs.org`,highlight:!0,zhNote:`VS Code / Slack / Discord / Notion 桌面端`,enNote:`VS Code / Slack / Discord / Notion desktops`},{name:`npm registry`,href:`https://www.npmjs.com`,zhNote:`npm 本身就是 Node 写的`,enNote:`npm itself is a Node app`},{name:`Stripe`,href:`https://stripe.com`,zhNote:`大量内部 Node 服务`,enNote:`Substantial internal Node services`},{name:`GitHub`,href:`https://github.com`,zhNote:`内部多个 Node 服务 + Octicons / Primer 前端`,enNote:`Multiple internal Node services + Octicons / Primer frontends`},{name:`Hono · Express · Fastify · Koa`,href:`https://hono.dev`,zhNote:`Node 上最常见的 web 框架`,enNote:`The most common web frameworks on Node`},{name:`TypeScript compiler`,href:`https://www.typescriptlang.org`,zhNote:`tsc 是个 Node 程序`,enNote:`tsc is a Node program`},{name:`pnpm · Turborepo`,href:`https://pnpm.io`,zhNote:`现代 monorepo 工具, 100% Node`,enNote:`Modern monorepo tooling, 100% Node`},{name:`Netflix`,href:`https://netflix.com`,zhNote:`API gateway / 客户端 SSR 部分用 Node`,enNote:`API gateway / client SSR pieces on Node`},{name:`Trello · Atlassian`,zhNote:`早期大规模 Node 实战之一`,enNote:`One of the earliest large-scale Node deployments`},{name:`cuberoot.me`,highlight:!0,zhNote:`本站 api.cuberoot.me Hono 服务跑在 Node 22.22.3`,enNote:`This site — api.cuberoot.me Hono server on Node 22.22.3`}],outlook:[{tag:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`HOT · 22 LTS`}),hot:!0,big:!0,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`22 LTS 是当下最稳的选择`}),body:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`Node 22 把 fetch / test / watch / --run / require(esm) / strip-types 一次性补齐, 同时给到 active LTS 到 2026-10、maintenance 到 2027-04-30 的支持窗口。`,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`新项目起步这是默认答案`}),`。`]}),(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`从 18 / 20 升 22 几乎是零摩擦:V8 12.4 + libuv 1.48, API breaking 极少。本站从 20 LTS 升 22 LTS 只改了 ecosystem.config.js 里的 node interpreter 路径。`})]})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`22 LTS is the most stable bet right now`}),body:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`Node 22 packed in fetch / test / watch / --run / require(esm) / strip-types in one release, with an active LTS until 2026-10 and maintenance until 2027-04-30. `,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`This is the default answer for new projects.`})]}),(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`Upgrading from 18 / 20 to 22 is nearly frictionless: V8 12.4 + libuv 1.48, with very few breaking changes. cuberoot.me moved from 20 LTS to 22 LTS by changing only the interpreter path in ecosystem.config.js.`})]})}},{tag:`24 LTS`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`下一条 LTS "Krypton"`}),body:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`2025-04 发布, V8 13.1 + npm 11 + AsyncLocalStorage 在 undici 里默认开启。性能基线 +10~15%, --strip-types 接近稳定。等 24 进 active LTS (2025-10) 后是下一个升级窗口。`})})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`The next LTS — "Krypton"`}),body:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`Released 2025-04 with V8 13.1, npm 11, and AsyncLocalStorage default in undici. Roughly +10–15% perf baseline and --strip-types close to stable. Once it enters active LTS (2025-10), it becomes the next reasonable upgrade window.`})})}},{tag:`COMPETITION`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Bun / Deno 的压力让 Node 改得最快`}),body:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`Bun 提供 4–10x cold start, 自带 bundler / tester / package manager。Deno 2 把 npm 兼容做扎实了。Node 没有装死, 反而是 18 → 22 这条线吸收得最快。竞品健康, 主线也跟着健康。`})})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Bun / Deno pressure made Node move fastest`}),body:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`Bun delivers 4–10x cold start with a built-in bundler / tester / package manager. Deno 2 shored up npm compatibility. Node didn't ossify — the 18 → 22 line absorbed lessons faster than anyone expected. Healthy competition, healthier mainline.`})})}},{tag:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`TYPES`}),zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`--strip-types 是 TS-on-Node 的终局`}),body:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`22 起的 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`--experimental-strip-types`}),` 把 TS 类型当注释跳过, 不做类型检查只剥语法 (跟 esbuild 一样)。等它稳定之后, dev 时 tsc / tsx / ts-node 这条工具链可以全删, prod 走 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`tsc`}),` 出类型 + .d.ts 做 IDE。`]})})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`--strip-types is the endgame for TS on Node`}),body:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`--experimental-strip-types`}),` (since 22) treats TS types as comments, stripping syntax without type-checking (the esbuild approach). Once stable, the tsc / tsx / ts-node dev toolchain can go away — prod uses `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`tsc`}),` to emit types + .d.ts for IDE, and runtime loads .ts directly.`]})})}},{tag:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`DATA`}),zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`npm 周下载 30 亿包`}),body:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`2026-05 数据:npm 周总下载 ~30 亿包, 注册包数 2.2M, 月活开发者按 GitHub Octoverse 估超过 1700 万。生态规模上其他运行时不在一个量级。`})})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`3B weekly package downloads on npm`}),body:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`2026-05 numbers: ~3B weekly downloads on npm, 2.2M registered packages, GitHub Octoverse estimates more than 17M monthly active developers. No other runtime is in this scale class.`})})}}],cuberoot:{zh:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`cuberoot.me 在云 VM 上跑`,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`一个 Node 22.22.3 进程`}),`, 监听 127.0.0.1:3001, nginx 反代 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`api.cuberoot.me`}),` 过来。pm2 fork 模式 (不开 cluster, 单机单 Hono 服务用不上), 进程崩了自动拉起。Node interpreter 装在 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`/usr/local/bin/node`}),`, 通过 nvm 管理多版本, 当前默认 22 LTS。`]}),(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`dev 这边不编译:`,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`tsx watch src/index.ts`}),` 直接跑 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`.ts`}),`, 改一个文件就重启。其实现在等 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`--experimental-strip-types`}),` 稳定之后 tsx 这层都可以删掉, 用 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`node --watch --experimental-strip-types src/index.ts`}),` 起服务。prod 走 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`tsc`}),` 编译到 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`dist/`}),`, pm2 启动 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`dist/index.js`}),`, 类型剥得很干净 (Hono 那条 RPC 类型链全靠 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`.d.ts`}),`)。`]}),(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`数据库连接走 porsager 的 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`postgres`}),` 包, Unix socket 连本地 PG13, 不走 TCP。这个包是纯 JS 实现, 没有 native binding, 升 Node 大版本不需要重编译。WCA OAuth / recon 缓存 / alg 库 / 训练数据这些端点的存储都在这条连接上。`]}),(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`启动持久化:`,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`pm2 startup`}),` + `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`pm2 save`}),` 把 pm2 写进 systemd, 服务器重启时 pm2-runtime 跟着起, 然后从 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`~/.pm2/dump.pm2`}),` 恢复 app 列表。日志走 pm2-logrotate, 单文件 10MB 滚, 保留 14 天, 落在 `,(0,t.jsxs)(`code`,{children:[`~/.pm2/logs/cuberoot-api-`,`{`,`out,err`,`}`,`.log`]}),`。整套部署单台机器自给自足, 没有 K8s 没有 Docker。`]})]}),en:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`cuberoot.me runs `,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`one Node 22.22.3 process`}),` on the cloud VM, bound to 127.0.0.1:3001, with nginx reverse-proxying `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`api.cuberoot.me`}),` in front. pm2 fork mode (no cluster — single Hono service on a single box doesn't need it); the process gets auto-restarted on crash. Node lives at `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`/usr/local/bin/node`}),`, managed by nvm, currently defaulting to 22 LTS.`]}),(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`Dev runs without compilation: `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`tsx watch src/index.ts`}),` runs `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`.ts`}),` directly with restart on save. Once `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`--experimental-strip-types`}),` stabilizes, the tsx layer can disappear in favor of `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`node --watch --experimental-strip-types src/index.ts`}),`. Prod uses `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`tsc`}),` to compile to `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`dist/`}),`, and pm2 starts `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`dist/index.js`}),`; the type system is fully stripped at runtime (the Hono RPC type chain lives in `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`.d.ts`}),`).`]}),(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`The database connection uses porsager's `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`postgres`}),` package over a Unix socket to local PG13, never TCP. It's a pure-JS implementation with no native binding — bumping Node majors doesn't require a rebuild. WCA OAuth, recon caches, alg library, training data — every endpoint's storage rides this one connection.`]}),(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`Boot persistence: `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`pm2 startup`}),` + `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`pm2 save`}),` writes pm2 into systemd; on server reboot, pm2-runtime starts via systemd and restores the app list from `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`~/.pm2/dump.pm2`}),`. Logs go through pm2-logrotate, rolling at 10MB per file with 14-day retention, landing in `,(0,t.jsxs)(`code`,{children:[`~/.pm2/logs/cuberoot-api-`,`{`,`out,err`,`}`,`.log`]}),`. The entire deployment is self-contained on one box — no K8s, no Docker.`]})]})},links:[{label:`nodejs.org`,href:`https://nodejs.org`},{label:`GitHub · nodejs/node`,href:`https://github.com/nodejs/node`},{label:`Node 22 LTS announcement`,href:`https://nodejs.org/en/blog/announcements/v22-release-announce`},{label:`22.22.3 release notes`,href:`https://nodejs.org/en/blog/release/v22.22.3`},{label:`LTS release schedule`,href:`https://github.com/nodejs/release#release-schedule`}]},{slug:`pm2`,name:`PM2`,version:`7.0`,since:`2013-06`,group:`backend`,accent:`#2B96EC`,bright:`#6FB9F2`,glyph:`P2`,floats:[`cluster`,`fork`,`reload`,`restart`,`startup`,`save`,`monit`,`logrotate`,`ecosystem`,`pm2 list`,`graceful`,`PID 1`],zh:{tagline:`Node 进程守护 + 集群 + 日志`,role:`把 Hono API 拉起来、崩了拉回去、reboot 后自动恢复, 全靠它一个 CLI。`,heroSub:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`Alexandre Strzelewicz 2013 年写出来, 解决一件事:Node 单进程崩了之后没人拉。十三年过去, pm2 包成了一个 cluster reload + 日志轮转 + 开机持久化 + 监控终端的全套。`,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`单机 Node 部署的事实标准。`})]}),whatDesc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`pm2 是一个`,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`进程管理器`}),`, 装在 Node 上, 围住一堆 Node 进程。它做四件事:守住进程 (崩了拉起)、零 downtime reload、日志收集 + 轮转、开机持久化 (systemd 集成)。`]}),historyDesc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`2013 年 npm 第一次发布时只是 "保 Node 进程活"。后来 cluster mode、ecosystem.config.js、pm2-runtime (Docker 友好 PID 1)、Keymetrics SaaS 一个个加。2025-05 的 v7.0 加上了 Bun 运行时支持, 把 pm2-axon / pm2-io-agent 内联进 monorepo, 减小供应链面。`}),conceptsTitle:`进程 + 配置 + 持久化`,conceptsDesc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`pm2 自己的 CLI 表面不大:启 / 停 / 重启 / reload / list / monit / logs / startup / save。配上 ecosystem.config.js 把 "几个 app、各自什么 env、几个 instance" 写死, 部署就是 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`pm2 reload ecosystem.config.js --env production`}),`。`]}),whyDesc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`2026 年单机 Node 部署还选 pm2, 不是因为它最酷, 而是因为:`,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`systemd 一个 unit 一个服务太繁琐`}),`, Docker / K8s 对单机一个 API 太重, forever 已死, foreman 偏 dev。pm2 这套刚好填中间。`]}),adoptersTitle:`谁在用`,adoptersDesc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`不上 K8s 的中小 Node 服务几乎人手一份 pm2。IBM cloud / DigitalOcean 的 Node 教程默认就用它。本站的 api.cuberoot.me 也是。`}),cuberootDesc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`本站 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`api.cuberoot.me`}),` Hono 服务在云 VM 上跑 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`pm2 start ecosystem.config.js`}),`, 一个 app, fork 模式, `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`pm2 startup`}),` + `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`pm2 save`}),` 注册到 systemd, 部署走 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`pm2 reload cuberoot-api`}),` 零 downtime。日志走 pm2-logrotate 滚 10MB / 留 14 天。`]}),outlookTitle:`当下与前景`,outlookDesc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`v7.0 把 Bun 支持加进来, 内化掉 pm2-axon / pm2-io-agent 减少供应链, 修 CVE。下一阶段 systemd / OpenRC 的二级集成, 以及对 Hono / Fastify 这一代框架的 metrics 自动接入会继续推。`})},en:{tagline:`Node process manager, cluster, and logs`,role:`Starts the Hono API, restarts it on crash, and brings it back after reboot — one CLI.`,heroSub:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`Alexandre Strzelewicz wrote pm2 in 2013 to solve one thing: when a single Node process crashes, nothing restarts it. Thirteen years later, pm2 wraps cluster reload + log rotation + boot persistence + a monitor TUI in one package. `,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`The de facto standard for single-host Node.`})]}),whatDesc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`pm2 is a `,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`process manager`}),` installed on top of Node, fencing in a set of Node processes. It does four things: keeps processes alive (restart on crash), zero-downtime reload, log collection + rotation, and boot persistence (systemd integration).`]}),historyDesc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`The 2013 first npm release just "kept Node alive." Cluster mode, ecosystem.config.js, pm2-runtime (Docker-friendly PID 1), and the Keymetrics SaaS arrived layer by layer. v7.0 in 2025-05 added Bun runtime support and inlined pm2-axon / pm2-io-agent to shrink supply-chain surface.`}),conceptsTitle:`Process + config + persistence`,conceptsDesc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`pm2's CLI surface is small: start / stop / restart / reload / list / monit / logs / startup / save. Combine with ecosystem.config.js to declare "which apps, which env, how many instances," and deploys become `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`pm2 reload ecosystem.config.js --env production`}),`.`]}),whyDesc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`Picking pm2 in 2026 for single-host Node isn't because it's the shiniest. It's because: `,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`writing a systemd unit per Node app is busywork`}),`, Docker / K8s is overkill for one API, forever is unmaintained, foreman is dev-oriented. pm2 fits the gap.`]}),adoptersTitle:`Who uses it`,adoptersDesc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Almost every small-to-mid Node service that doesn't run K8s ships with pm2. IBM Cloud / DigitalOcean Node tutorials default to it. So does cuberoot.me's api.`}),cuberootDesc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`cuberoot.me's `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`api.cuberoot.me`}),` Hono service runs `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`pm2 start ecosystem.config.js`}),` on the cloud VM — one app, fork mode, `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`pm2 startup`}),` + `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`pm2 save`}),` registered with systemd. Deploys run `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`pm2 reload cuberoot-api`}),` for zero-downtime restart, logs go through pm2-logrotate (10MB roll / 14-day retention).`]}),outlookTitle:`Now and next`,outlookDesc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`v7.0 added Bun support, inlined pm2-axon / pm2-io-agent for a smaller supply chain, and shipped CVE fixes. The next phase is deeper systemd / OpenRC integration and auto-metrics for the Hono / Fastify generation of frameworks.`})},heroStats:[{num:`7`,unit:`.0.1`,zh:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`当前稳定版 `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`2025-05-02 · v7.0.1`})]}),en:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`current stable `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`2025-05-02 · v7.0.1`})]})},{num:`13`,unit:`y`,zh:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`从 2013 至今 `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`Node 守护事实标准`})]}),en:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`since 2013 `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`de facto Node supervisor`})]})},{num:`0`,unit:`s`,zh:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`graceful reload downtime `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`cluster mode`})]}),en:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`graceful reload downtime `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`cluster mode`})]})},{num:`40`,unit:`k★`,zh:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`GitHub Unitech/pm2 `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`2026-05`})]}),en:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`GitHub Unitech/pm2 `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`2026-05`})]})}],intro:{zh:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`pm2 2013-06-27 第一次发布到 npm, 作者 Alexandre Strzelewicz, 当时 Node 还在 0.10 时代。问题很具体:你在云 VM 上跑一个 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`node app.js`}),`, 它崩了就没了, 没人拉起来。社区有 forever、nodemon、supervisor 各自塞一块, 但都不太完整。Strzelewicz 把 "进程守护 + 自动重启 + 日志收集 + CLI" 一次性打包成 pm2, 起步就清楚地比对手好用。`]}),(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`之后是一连串能力扩展。2014 cluster mode 上线 —— pm2 启动多个 Node worker, 走内置 round-robin LB, reload 时一个一个换不掉请求。2015 ecosystem.config.js 把 "几个 app、什么 env、几个 instance" 配置化, 部署变成一行 reload。2017 pm2-runtime 出来, 在容器里取代 daemon, 作为 PID 1 直接 exec (Docker 友好)。2020 年 Keymetrics 商业监控关停, OSS 继续走。`}),(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`2025-05 v7.0 / 7.0.1 是个比较大的 cut:Node 18+ baseline, `,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`加 Bun 运行时支持`}),`, 把 pm2-axon / pm2-io-agent 内化进 monorepo (减小供应链面 + 修一批 CVE)。本站 prod 跑的就是这版 (Node 22.22.3 + pm2 7.0.1 + ecosystem.config.js fork 单实例)。`]})]}),en:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`pm2 first published to npm on 2013-06-27. Author: Alexandre Strzelewicz; Node was still at 0.10. The problem was concrete: you run `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`node app.js`}),` on a cloud VM and when it crashes, nothing restarts it. The community had forever, nodemon, supervisor each covering a piece, but nothing felt complete. Strzelewicz packaged "process supervision + auto-restart + log capture + CLI" together as pm2 — meaningfully better than the alternatives from day one.`]}),(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`What followed was a long capability ramp. 2014 added cluster mode — pm2 forks N Node workers with an internal round-robin LB, replacing them one at a time on reload without dropping requests. 2015 added ecosystem.config.js to declare "which apps, which env, which instance counts," reducing deploys to one reload command. 2017 brought pm2-runtime, which replaces the daemon fork inside containers as PID 1 (Docker-friendly). 2020 saw the Keymetrics monitoring SaaS shut down; OSS kept going.`}),(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`2025-05's v7.0 / 7.0.1 was a sizeable cut: Node 18+ baseline, `,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`added Bun runtime support`}),`, inlined pm2-axon / pm2-io-agent into the monorepo (smaller supply-chain surface + a wave of CVE fixes). This site's prod runs exactly this release (Node 22.22.3 + pm2 7.0.1 + an ecosystem.config.js with one fork-mode instance).`]})]})},history:[{year:`2013·06`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`v0.x — 首次 npm 发布`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Alexandre Strzelewicz 上传 pm2 0.x, 解决 "Node 进程崩了没人拉" 这一件事。CLI 起步就是 start / stop / restart / list 几个。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`v0.x — first npm publish`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Alexandre Strzelewicz publishes pm2 0.x, solving the single problem of "Node crashed, nothing restarts it." Initial CLI is start / stop / restart / list.`})}},{year:`2014`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Cluster 模式上线`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`pm2 fork 多个 worker, 走 Node 内置 round-robin 负载均衡, reload 时一个一个换, 请求不掉。从此单机多核 Node 服务有了真正可用的方案。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Cluster mode lands`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`pm2 forks N workers behind Node's built-in round-robin balancer; reload swaps workers one at a time, no dropped requests. Single-host multi-core Node services finally had a real answer.`})}},{year:`2014·09`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Keymetrics SaaS`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Unitech 推出 Keymetrics, 把 pm2 进程的指标 (CPU / mem / latency) 上送到一个 web 监控面板。OSS pm2 留下钩子。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Keymetrics SaaS`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Unitech launches Keymetrics, streaming pm2 process metrics (CPU / mem / latency) to a hosted web dashboard. OSS pm2 keeps the hooks.`})}},{year:`2015`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`ecosystem.config.js`}),desc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`声明式配置文件:把 "几个 app、各自 script、env、instance 数" 写一份, 部署就是 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`pm2 reload ecosystem.config.js`}),`。多 app 多 env 终于不靠脚本拼。`]})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`ecosystem.config.js`}),desc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`Declarative config: "which apps, which scripts, which envs, how many instances" live in one file; a deploy becomes `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`pm2 reload ecosystem.config.js`}),`. No more multi-app shell glue.`]})}},{year:`2017`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`pm2-runtime`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Docker-友好版:不 fork daemon, 直接作为 PID 1 在容器里 exec Node。容器化部署的标准入口点。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`pm2-runtime`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`The Docker-friendly variant: no daemon fork, run as PID 1 inside the container and exec Node directly. The default entrypoint for containerized deploys.`})}},{year:`2020`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Keymetrics 监控关停`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Unitech 关掉 Keymetrics 商业 SaaS, 转回 OSS 与企业自托管。CLI / 模块全部留下, 没有断供。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Keymetrics monitoring shuts down`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Unitech retires the Keymetrics SaaS, pivots to OSS and self-hosted enterprise. The CLI / modules continue uninterrupted.`})}},{year:`2023·04`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`v5.0 — 现代化内核`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`内部代码大整, Node 16+ baseline。pm2-logrotate / pm2 monit / pm2 deploy 三个核心模块同步升级。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`v5.0 — modernized internals`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Significant internal cleanup, Node 16+ baseline. pm2-logrotate / pm2 monit / pm2 deploy refreshed in lockstep.`})}},{year:`2024`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`v6.x`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Node 18+ baseline, pm2-logrotate 稳定性显著改善 —— 之前在高 QPS 下偶尔丢一段日志的 bug 修了。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`v6.x`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Node 18+ baseline; pm2-logrotate stability meaningfully improves — a long-standing "lose a log segment under high QPS" bug finally closed.`})}},{year:`2025·05`,highlight:!0,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`v7.0 / 7.0.1`}),desc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`Node 18+ baseline、`,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`加 Bun runtime 支持`}),`、内化 pm2-axon / pm2-io-agent 减小供应链面、修一批 CVE。本站 prod 就跑这版。`]})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`v7.0 / 7.0.1`}),desc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`Node 18+ baseline, `,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`added Bun runtime support`}),`, inlined pm2-axon / pm2-io-agent to shrink supply-chain surface, plus a CVE-fix wave. This is what cuberoot.me's prod runs.`]})}},{year:`2026·05`,highlight:!0,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`当前稳定 v7.0.1`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`7.0.1 是本年最广泛部署的稳定版本。GitHub Unitech/pm2 ~40k star, npm 周下载 ~150 万。单机 Node 守护这条路上没有同量级对手。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Current stable v7.0.1`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`7.0.1 is the most widely deployed stable in 2026. ~40k stars on GitHub (Unitech/pm2), ~1.5M weekly downloads on npm. No comparable competitor for single-host Node supervision.`})}}],concepts:[{tag:`A`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`start + 守护`}),desc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`pm2 start app.js --name myapp`}),` 把进程托管, 崩了自动重启 (默认无限次, 可设上限和退避)。`]})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`start + supervise`}),desc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[(