`,c(`// LLMs almost always succeed`)]})}],adopters:[{name:`GitHub Actions`,href:`https://docs.github.com/actions`,highlight:!0,zhNote:`每个 runner 跑容器, Docker action 是一等公民`,enNote:`Every runner runs containers; Docker actions are first-class`},{name:`GitLab CI`,href:`https://docs.gitlab.com/ee/ci/`,zhNote:`每个 job 默认 docker executor`,enNote:`Every CI job defaults to a docker executor`},{name:`Kubernetes`,href:`https://kubernetes.io`,highlight:!0,zhNote:`OCI 镜像就是 K8s 的部署单元`,enNote:`OCI images are the K8s deploy unit`},{name:`Fly.io`,href:`https://fly.io`,zhNote:`Dockerfile → 全球边缘 VM, 一键部署`,enNote:`Dockerfile → global edge VMs in one command`},{name:`Render`,href:`https://render.com`,zhNote:`PaaS, 接 Dockerfile / 仓库自动构建`,enNote:`PaaS that auto-builds from Dockerfile / repo`},{name:`Railway`,href:`https://railway.app`,zhNote:`Heroku 风 PaaS, 容器化为底`,enNote:`Heroku-style PaaS, container-native underneath`},{name:`Vercel build container`,href:`https://vercel.com`,zhNote:`build 阶段每个项目跑独立容器`,enNote:`Each project builds inside its own container`},{name:`HuggingFace Spaces`,href:`https://huggingface.co/spaces`,zhNote:`Docker SDK 选项支撑自定义 ML demo`,enNote:`Docker SDK option powers custom ML demos`},{name:`Claude Code sandbox`,href:`https://github.com/anthropics/claude-code`,zhNote:`Anthropic CLI 的隔离执行环境基于容器`,enNote:`The agent’s isolated execution layer is container-based`},{name:`Postgres Hub image`,href:`https://hub.docker.com/_/postgres`,zhNote:`官方镜像月拉取 5 亿+, 业内常态`,enNote:`500M+ pulls/month on the official image — table stakes`},{name:`nginx Hub image`,href:`https://hub.docker.com/_/nginx`,zhNote:`同上, web server 标配运行方式`,enNote:`Same scale — the standard way to ship a web server`},{name:`Testcontainers`,href:`https://testcontainers.com`,zhNote:`测试时按需起真实 PG/Kafka, 不再 mock`,enNote:`Spin up real PG/Kafka during tests — no more mocks`},{name:`cuberoot.me`,highlight:!0,zhNote:`本机 pg13 容器做 schema / migration dry-run`,enNote:`Local pg13 container for schema / migration dry-runs`}],outlook:[{tag:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`HOT · 2026-02`}),hot:!0,big:!0,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Engine 29 — containerd image store 默认`}),body:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`v29 是个分水岭:新装机默认走 containerd image store, classic graphdriver 进入维护模式。意味着 Docker / Kubernetes / nerdctl 三家终于在 image storage 这一层完全同源, 镜像 push/pull 行为更可预测, OCI artifact 这种"不止是容器镜像"的对象 (helm chart / WASM 模块) 也能放进来。`}),(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`同时最低 API 升到 1.44, v25 以下 EOL。生产端在升级前必须 audit 一下还有没有客户端在用老 API。`})]})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Engine 29 — containerd image store default`}),body:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`v29 is a watershed: the containerd image store is the new-install default; the classic graphdriver enters maintenance. Docker / Kubernetes / nerdctl finally share the same image-storage layer, push / pull becomes more predictable, and OCI artifacts (helm charts, WASM modules — not only container images) can live in the same store.`}),(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`The minimum API bumps to 1.44 and anything below v25 is EOL. Production sites should audit for old API clients before upgrading.`})]})}},{tag:`BUILD`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`BuildKit + zstd + nydus`}),body:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`BuildKit 已经是默认 builder。下一步是 zstd 压缩层 (拉取速度提升 30-50%) 和 nydus 这类按需加载的 lazy image format —— 镜像数 GB 但启动只下到刚开机要用的几十 MB。冷启动 / serverless 容器场景受益最大。`})})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`BuildKit + zstd + nydus`}),body:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`BuildKit is already the default builder. Next stops are zstd-compressed layers (30-50% pull speedup) and on-demand image formats like nydus — multi-GB images that fetch only the tens of MB needed at boot. Cold-start and serverless containers benefit the most.`})})}},{tag:`DAEMONLESS`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Podman / nerdctl 在 dev 端起来`}),body:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`Docker Desktop 2022 收费后, 大公司开发机批量迁到 Podman (无 daemon, 用户态 rootless) 和 Rancher Desktop / Orbstack。镜像格式没变, CLI 子集 兼容, 迁移成本只在 dev 端。生产端依然 containerd / K8s, 大局未变。`})})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Daemonless gains on dev`}),body:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`After Docker Desktop's 2022 license change, large companies migrated dev machines to Podman (no daemon, rootless) and Rancher Desktop / Orbstack. Image format stays, CLI subsets overlap; the cost lives on dev only. Production is still containerd / K8s — no shift there.`})})}},{tag:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`SECURITY`}),zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`rootless + 镜像签名常态化`}),body:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`Rootless container (Docker 20.10+ / Podman) 在生产逐步默认开;镜像签名 (cosign / sigstore) 成为合规要求。Supply chain 攻击面被压窄, 但需要 CI 改写流水线 —— "build → sign → push → admission controller verify" 四步成新标准。`})})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Rootless + signed images go mainstream`}),body:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`Rootless containers (Docker 20.10+ / Podman) become a production default; image signing (cosign / sigstore) becomes a compliance baseline. Supply-chain surface narrows, but CI pipelines must change: "build → sign → push → admission-controller verify" is the new four-step standard.`})})}},{tag:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`AI`}),zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Model Runner + MCP Toolkit`}),body:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`Docker Desktop 4.x 加进 Docker Model Runner (本地跑 LLM, 支持 vLLM Metal / CUDA) 和 MCP Toolkit (管理 MCP server 集合)。把 "用容器跑 AI 模型" 推到本地默认体验。和 Ollama / LM Studio 这些专用工具竞争, 但赌的是开发者已经熟 docker CLI 这一点。`})})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Model Runner + MCP Toolkit`}),body:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`Docker Desktop 4.x adds Docker Model Runner (run LLMs locally with vLLM Metal / CUDA) and the MCP Toolkit (manage MCP server collections). "Container runs the AI model" becomes the default local experience. Competes with Ollama / LM Studio, betting on developer familiarity with the docker CLI.`})})}}],cuberoot:{zh:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`cuberoot.me 用 Docker 的范围非常窄, 只在`,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`本地开发机`}),`。开发依赖的 PostgreSQL 13 在生产 VM 上是裸装进程, 本地用一个常驻容器 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`pg13`}),` 跑同版本镜像, 端口映 5433、密码 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`dev`}),`、数据库 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`cuberoot_db`}),`, 用来在改 schema / 写 migration / 调 load.sql 时先打一遍。生产 PG 升或加索引前, 同样的 SQL 先在这个容器里跑通, 才考虑往 prod 推。`]}),(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`生产 VM `,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`没有用 Docker`}),`。nginx 是 systemd 管的原生服务, Hono API 是 pm2 启动的 Node 进程, PostgreSQL 13 是 apt / dnf 装的原生数据库。原因是单机部署、流量规模有限、运维只一个人, 多加一层容器化只会增加调试链路 (日志位置 / 网络命名空间 / volume 挂载) 而没有任何收益。等什么时候要横向扩到第二台机器、需要 image rollback 时再考虑容器化。`]}),(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`CI 这块, GitHub Actions runner 本身就跑在容器里, 所以 stats-build 流水线 (压几十 GB 的 WCA dump、跑 SQL、产出 JSON) 是天然 isolated 的, 不需要本地 Docker 介入。client typecheck / test 也是 runner 的 ephemeral 容器环境, 完了即丢。`}),(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`个人开发还有一个常见用法是用 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`docker run --rm`}),` 起一次性的 utility 容器 (临时跑个 jq / yq / pandoc / 不想装到主机的 CLI), 但这跟 cuberoot.me 这个项目本身没强绑定。`]})]}),en:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`cuberoot.me uses Docker narrowly — `,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`only on the dev machine`}),`. Production PostgreSQL 13 runs as a bare process on the VM; locally a long-lived container `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`pg13`}),` runs the matching image with port 5433, password `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`dev`}),`, database `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`cuberoot_db`}),`. Whenever a schema change, migration, or load.sql tweak is in flight, it gets dry-run against this container first. Anything destined for prod PG (column adds, new indexes) clears the local container before being pushed.`]}),(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`The production VM `,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`does not run Docker`}),`. nginx is a native systemd service, the Hono API is a Node process managed by pm2, PostgreSQL 13 is the distro-package install. The reasoning: single-host deploy, modest traffic, single-operator ops — adding a container layer would only stretch the debug path (log paths, network namespaces, volume mounts) for zero gain. The day this site scales to a second machine or wants image rollbacks, containerization moves on the table.`]}),(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`For CI, GitHub Actions runners are themselves containerized, so the stats-build pipeline (chewing through multi-GB WCA dumps, running SQL, emitting JSON) is naturally isolated — no local Docker required. Client typecheck / test run in the same ephemeral runner containers.`}),(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`One adjacent dev habit is firing one-shot utility containers with `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`docker run --rm`}),` (jq / yq / pandoc / random CLI you don't want on the host), but that's not specific to this project.`]})]})},links:[{label:`docker.com`,href:`https://www.docker.com`},{label:`GitHub · moby/moby`,href:`https://github.com/moby/moby`},{label:`Docker Engine v29 release notes`,href:`https://docs.docker.com/engine/release-notes/29/`},{label:`Docker Desktop release notes`,href:`https://docs.docker.com/desktop/release-notes/`},{label:`OCI spec`,href:`https://opencontainers.org`}]},{slug:`systemd`,name:`systemd`,version:`260`,since:`2010-03`,group:`backend`,accent:`#30D475`,bright:`#5EE89C`,glyph:`⌬`,floats:[`PID 1`,`.service`,`.timer`,`.socket`,`.mount`,`journald`,`logind`,`networkd`,`resolved`,`systemctl`,`journalctl`,`unit`,`cgroup`],zh:{tagline:`PID 1 + 服务管理 + 日志 + 定时器`,role:`云服务器上跑 cuberoot.me 整套后端: nginx、pm2、pg-dump 备份、acme.sh 续证全是 systemd unit。`,heroSub:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`Linux 启动后第一个跑的进程, 也是几乎所有后台服务的爹。把 SysV init 那一堆 shell 脚本换成`,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`声明式 unit 文件`}),`, 顺手把日志、定时任务、网络配置、cgroup 资源限制全装进同一棵进程树。Lennart Poettering 2010 年在 Red Hat 抛出这一脚, 十六年后, 主流 Linux 发行版几乎没有不用它的。`]}),whatDesc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`systemd 不是单纯的 init, 而是一组共用 D-Bus / cgroup / unit 模型的系统组件:`,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`PID 1`}),` 拉服务, `,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`journald`}),` 收日志, `,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`timer`}),` 替代 cron, `,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`networkd / resolved`}),` 管网络, `,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`logind`}),` 管登录会话。统一的 unit 配置 + `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`systemctl`}),` 一个命令面板, 让运维心智从"哪个脚本在哪个目录"变成"哪个 unit 处于什么状态"。`]}),historyDesc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`2010 年从 "Rethinking PID 1" 那篇博客起步, 2011 年 Fedora 第一个默认启用。2014 年 Debian 那场"要不要切 systemd"的辩论是 Linux 社区近十年最激烈的一次。打完之后 Debian 8、Ubuntu 15.04、RHEL 7、Arch、SUSE 全跟上。现在 "Linux 服务器" 和 "systemd" 基本是同义词。`}),conceptsTitle:`Unit + systemctl 核心`,conceptsDesc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`所有可被 systemd 管的东西都叫 `,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`unit`}),`: service / socket / timer / mount / path / target 六种最常用。配置是 ini 风格的纯文本, `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`systemctl`}),` 是统一的查询 + 控制入口。`]}),whyDesc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`2026 年还在用 systemd, 不是因为它"最小巧", 而是因为它把`,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`服务管理 + 日志 + 定时 + 资源隔离 + 网络`}),`五件事用同一套模型做了, 运维只学一遍, 不必再背 init.d / cron / syslog / iptables 各自的命令。`]}),adoptersTitle:`谁在用`,adoptersDesc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`除了 Alpine / Void / Gentoo 这几个故意不用的, 主流 Linux 发行版几乎清一色 systemd。云厂商默认镜像、嵌入式 Linux 设备、车载 Linux 大多走这一套。`}),cuberootDesc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`cuberoot.me 的云服务器整台都靠 systemd 拉起来。nginx 作为 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`nginx.service`}),` 被它看着, pm2 自己又通过 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`pm2 startup`}),` 装成一个 systemd unit 进而托管 Hono。`,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`pg-dump-recon.timer`}),` 每天 03:00 UTC 触发一次, 把 PG dump 落到 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`/root/archive/`}),`, 留 30 天。acme.sh 的证书续期也走 systemd timer, 不用 cron。机器一出问题, 第一个命令就是 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`journalctl -u xxx -f`}),`。`]}),outlookTitle:`当下与前景`,outlookDesc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`systemd 260 刚把 SysV 兼容代码彻底删干净, kernel 最低支持上抬到 5.10。后面的路线是把更多原本散在第三方的东西 (sysext / confext / homed / portabled) 也整合进同一套 unit 抽象。container / VM 边界继续模糊, "一个 host 跑一堆轻量 namespace" 是默认范式。`})},en:{tagline:`PID 1 + service manager + journal + timers`,role:`Runs the whole cuberoot.me VM — nginx, pm2, the pg-dump backup, and acme.sh renewals are all systemd units.`,heroSub:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`The first process Linux starts at boot, and the parent of nearly every background service. Replace the SysV init shell jungle with `,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`declarative unit files`}),`, then fold logging, timers, network config, and cgroup resource limits into the same process tree. Lennart Poettering shipped that idea at Red Hat in 2010; sixteen years later, nearly every mainstream Linux distro runs it.`]}),whatDesc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`systemd isn't just an init — it's a family of components sharing one D-Bus / cgroup / unit model: `,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`PID 1`}),` brings up services, `,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`journald`}),` captures logs, `,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`timers`}),` replace cron, `,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`networkd / resolved`}),` handle networking, `,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`logind`}),` tracks sessions. One unit file format + one `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`systemctl`}),` control plane turns ops from "which script lives in which directory" into "what state is this unit in."`]}),historyDesc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`The story starts with the 2010 "Rethinking PID 1" blog post; Fedora was the first to default to it in 2011. Debian's 2014 init-system debate over whether to adopt systemd was the loudest Linux community fight of the decade. Once it settled, Debian 8, Ubuntu 15.04, RHEL 7, Arch, and SUSE all followed. Today "Linux server" and "systemd" are roughly synonymous.`}),conceptsTitle:`Units + systemctl core`,conceptsDesc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`Everything systemd manages is a `,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`unit`}),`: service / socket / timer / mount / path / target are the common six. Configuration is plain ini-style text; `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`systemctl`}),` is the single query + control entry point.`]}),whyDesc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`Still using systemd in 2026 isn't because it's "minimal" — it's because `,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`service management + logging + scheduling + resource isolation + networking`}),` all share one model. Ops learns it once instead of memorizing init.d / cron / syslog / iptables separately.`]}),adoptersTitle:`Who uses it`,adoptersDesc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Apart from Alpine / Void / Gentoo, which deliberately opt out, mainstream Linux distros run systemd uniformly. Cloud provider default images, embedded Linux devices, and automotive Linux mostly ride the same stack.`}),cuberootDesc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`The cuberoot.me VM is brought up entirely by systemd. nginx runs as `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`nginx.service`}),`, and pm2 — installed via `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`pm2 startup`}),` — is itself a systemd unit that in turn supervises the Hono server. `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`pg-dump-recon.timer`}),` fires daily at 03:00 UTC, dumping PG into `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`/root/archive/`}),` with 30-day retention. acme.sh certificate renewals also ride a systemd timer rather than cron. When anything misbehaves, the first command typed is `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`journalctl -u xxx -f`}),`.`]}),outlookTitle:`Now and next`,outlookDesc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`systemd 260 just removed the last SysV compat code and raised the minimum kernel to 5.10. The roadmap keeps absorbing things that used to live in third-party tools (sysext / confext / homed / portabled) into the same unit abstraction. The container / VM boundary continues to blur; "one host runs a swarm of lightweight namespaces" is now the default pattern.`})},heroStats:[{num:`260`,zh:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`当前稳定版 `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`2026-03 · systemd 260`})]}),en:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`current stable `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`2026-03 · systemd 260`})]})},{num:`16`,unit:`y`,zh:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`从 2010 至今 `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`主流 Linux 发行版默认 init`})]}),en:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`since 2010 `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`default init across mainstream distros`})]})},{num:`#1`,zh:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`Linux init 系统市占 `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`主流发行版几乎全用`})]}),en:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`Linux init by share `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`basically every mainstream distro`})]})},{num:`6`,zh:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`主流 unit 类型 `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`service / socket / timer / mount / path / target`})]}),en:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`common unit types `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`service / socket / timer / mount / path / target`})]})}],intro:{zh:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`systemd 起源于 2010 年 4 月 Lennart Poettering 在 Red Hat 写的一篇博客 "Rethinking PID 1"。他当时已经因为 PulseAudio / Avahi 出过名, 这次想解决的是 Linux 启动那一堆 SysV init shell 脚本: 串行、依赖关系藏在脚本注释里、出错了只能 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`cat /var/log/messages`}),` 翻。设想很直接: 把 init 重写成一个能`,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`并行拉服务、用声明式配置、能跑事件循环`}),`的 PID 1, 顺手把日志和定时也接管了。`]}),(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`2011 年 Fedora 15 第一个默认启用 systemd, 替掉了 Upstart。这之后是几年大规模社区争吵 —— 2014 年 Debian 那场"切不切 systemd"的投票是 Linux 近十年最激烈的辩论之一, 持反对意见的 Devuan 等分叉至今还活着, 但主流 Debian 8 (2015)、Ubuntu 15.04、RHEL 7、Arch、SUSE 全切了过来。`}),(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`Poettering 2022 年 9 月从 Red Hat 跳去 Microsoft 继续做 systemd, Kay Sievers 这边一直在维护底层组件。版本号在 2018 年前后切到纯数字 (一年一个大版本), 现在 (2026-03) 是 260, 把 SysV service 脚本兼容代码全删了 —— 16 年过去, 这层兼容终于不需要了。`})]}),en:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`systemd started as an April 2010 blog post by Lennart Poettering at Red Hat — "Rethinking PID 1." He was already known for PulseAudio and Avahi; this time the target was the SysV init shell jungle that handled Linux boot: serial execution, dependencies hidden in script comments, and "`,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`cat /var/log/messages`}),`" as the debugging tool. The proposal was direct: rewrite init as a PID 1 that `,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`brings services up in parallel, takes declarative config, and runs an event loop`}),`, while also subsuming logging and scheduling.`]}),(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`Fedora 15 (2011) was the first to default to systemd, displacing Upstart. The next few years were a community brawl — Debian's 2014 vote on whether to switch was the loudest Linux argument of the decade. The Devuan fork still exists, but mainstream Debian 8 (2015), Ubuntu 15.04, RHEL 7, Arch, and SUSE all moved over.`}),(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`Poettering moved from Red Hat to Microsoft in September 2022 and kept working on systemd; Kay Sievers stayed on the lower-level components. The version scheme switched to plain integers around 2018 (one major a year). As of 2026-03 it's at 260, which finally removed the SysV service-script compatibility code — sixteen years on, that compat layer is no longer needed.`})]})},history:[{year:`2010·04`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`"Rethinking PID 1"`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Lennart Poettering 在 Red Hat 发博客, 把 SysV init 串行 + shell 脚本 + 隐式依赖的问题摊开, 抛出并行 + 声明式 + 事件循环的新设计。Kay Sievers 同期参与。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`"Rethinking PID 1"`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Lennart Poettering's Red Hat blog post lays out the SysV init pain — serial boot, shell scripts, implicit deps — and proposes a parallel, declarative, event-loop-driven replacement. Kay Sievers joins in parallel.`})}},{year:`2011·05`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Fedora 15 默认启用`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Fedora 第一个主流发行版把 systemd 设为默认 init, 替掉 Upstart。并行启动让冷启动时间立刻降一档, 外界开始认真看待这个项目。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Fedora 15 ships it by default`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Fedora becomes the first mainstream distro to default to systemd, displacing Upstart. Parallel boot cuts cold-start time noticeably; the outside world starts taking it seriously.`})}},{year:`2012·09`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`journald 落地`}),desc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`systemd-journald 接管系统日志, 结构化 + 索引 + 二进制存储, `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`journalctl`}),` 替代翻 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`/var/log/messages`}),` 的工作流。`]})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`journald lands`}),desc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`systemd-journald takes over system logging — structured, indexed, binary storage. `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`journalctl`}),` replaces grepping through `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`/var/log/messages`}),`.`]})}},{year:`2014·02`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Debian init 之战`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Debian Technical Committee 投票决定下一代默认 init。最终 systemd 8:7 险胜 Upstart。Devuan 等反对派分叉出去。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`The Debian init war`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Debian's Technical Committee votes on the next default init. systemd wins 8:7 over Upstart. The Devuan fork emerges from the dissent.`})}},{year:`2014·12`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`RHEL 7 + Debian 8`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`RHEL 7 (12 月) + 即将到来的 Debian 8 (Jessie) 都切到 systemd。企业 Linux 这条线正式定调。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`RHEL 7 + Debian 8`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`RHEL 7 (December) and the imminent Debian 8 (Jessie) both adopt systemd. The enterprise Linux line is set.`})}},{year:`2015·04`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Ubuntu 15.04 切换`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Ubuntu 从自家 Upstart 切到 systemd。Canonical 自此把精力从 init 重新投回上层应用。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Ubuntu 15.04 switches`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Ubuntu drops its in-house Upstart for systemd. Canonical redirects effort from init back into higher layers.`})}},{year:`2016·07`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`v231 — 大版本号时代`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`版本号简化到纯整数, 一年一个大版本。socket activation、networkd、resolved、logind 全部稳定下来。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`v231 — plain-integer versions`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Version numbers simplify to plain integers, one major per year. socket activation, networkd, resolved, logind all stabilize.`})}},{year:`2018·06`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`v239 — DynamicUser`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`DynamicUser= 让 service 跑时临时分配 UID, 跑完释放。"按需创建一次性账户"的隔离粒度开始下沉到 unit 文件里。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`v239 — DynamicUser`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`DynamicUser= lets a service get an ephemeral UID for the duration of its run. Per-unit ephemeral-account isolation lands.`})}},{year:`2020·12`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`v247 — homed / portabled`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`systemd-homed 把用户家目录变成可移动的加密 image, portabled 让服务可以打成自包含 image 跨主机搬。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`v247 — homed / portabled`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`systemd-homed turns home directories into portable encrypted images; portabled lets services ship as self-contained images that move between hosts.`})}},{year:`2022·09`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Poettering 跳槽 Microsoft`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Lennart Poettering 离开 Red Hat 加入 Microsoft, 继续做 systemd 主线开发。被 Linux 社区视为又一轮"巨头收编"事件, 但发行版没有任何变化。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Poettering moves to Microsoft`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Lennart Poettering leaves Red Hat for Microsoft, continuing as systemd's main developer. The Linux community calls it another "big-vendor capture" moment; distros change nothing.`})}},{year:`2024·07`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`v256 — run0 + 容器化`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`v256 推出 run0