`,c(`// breaking changes: rare, deprecated for years first`)]})}],adopters:[{name:`Linux kernel`,href:`https://kernel.org`,highlight:!0,zhNote:`Git 的起源仓库, Linus 仍然用它接收 patch`,enNote:`The repo Git was written for — Linus still uses it to accept patches`},{name:`GitHub`,href:`https://github.com`,highlight:!0,zhNote:`把 Git 推上主流的 web forge, 现 1.5 亿用户`,enNote:`The web forge that pushed Git into the mainstream — 150M+ users`},{name:`GitLab`,href:`https://gitlab.com`,highlight:!0,zhNote:`自托管 + SaaS 双轨, 企业 git 主力`,enNote:`Self-hosted + SaaS — the enterprise git default`},{name:`Chromium`,href:`https://chromium.googlesource.com/chromium/src`,zhNote:`~3000 万行 C++, 重度 git 用户`,enNote:`~30M lines of C++; heavy git user`},{name:`Android`,href:`https://android.googlesource.com`,zhNote:`通过 repo 工具组织上百个 git 子仓`,enNote:`Hundreds of git sub-repos coordinated via the repo tool`},{name:`LLVM / Rust / Go / Python`,zhNote:`主流编译器 / 语言项目全部 git`,enNote:`All major compiler / language projects on git`},{name:`Sourcehut`,href:`https://sourcehut.org`,zhNote:`Drew DeVault 的极简 forge, email-driven workflow`,enNote:`Drew DeVault's minimalist forge, email-driven workflow`},{name:`Gitea / Forgejo`,href:`https://gitea.com`,zhNote:`轻量自托管 forge, 大量 homelab 在用`,enNote:`Lightweight self-hosted forges, popular for homelabs`},{name:`Codeberg`,href:`https://codeberg.org`,zhNote:`非营利 OSS forge, 基于 Forgejo`,enNote:`Non-profit OSS forge built on Forgejo`},{name:`Sapling (Meta)`,href:`https://sapling-scm.com`,zhNote:`Meta 2022 年从 Mercurial 迁过来的 git-兼容 VCS`,enNote:`Meta's git-compatible VCS, replaced Mercurial in 2022`},{name:`Anthropic Claude Code`,href:`https://github.com/anthropics/claude-code`,highlight:!0,zhNote:`AI agent 默认在 git repo 内工作`,enNote:`AI agent designed to work inside git repos by default`},{name:`cuberoot.me`,highlight:!0,zhNote:`本仓库 — 单一 git 树托管 24 工具 + server + ops`,enNote:`This repo — a single git tree for 24 tools + server + ops`}],outlook:[{tag:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`HOT · 2026-04`}),hot:!0,big:!0,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`SHA-256 从实验性 → 可选默认`}),body:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`2.54 把 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`--object-format=sha256`}),` 从 "实验性" 提到 "新仓库可选默认"。GitHub / GitLab / Sourcehut 服务端的 SHA-256-aware 协议在 2025 年下半年陆续就绪, 新建 repo 终于可以走 SHA-256 + 双向 push 到主流 forge。`]}),(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`SHA-1 不会立刻消失 — 老仓库迁移涉及所有引用此 SHA 的外部系统 (commit URL / build pipeline / package manager lock 文件), 现实路径是"新仓库 sha256, 老仓库长期 sha1 共存"。但路终于通了。`})]})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`SHA-256: experimental → opt-in default`}),body:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`2.54 promotes `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`--object-format=sha256`}),` from "experimental" to "opt-in default for new repos." Server-side SHA-256-aware protocols on GitHub / GitLab / Sourcehut came online through late 2025, so new repos can finally go SHA-256 with bidirectional push to mainstream forges.`]}),(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`SHA-1 isn't going away soon — migrating old repos touches everything that references a SHA (commit URLs / CI pipelines / package lockfiles). The realistic path is "new repos on SHA-256, old repos stay SHA-1 long-term." But the path is open.`})]})}},{tag:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`HOT`}),hot:!0,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Jujutsu (jj) 抢 UX 之心`}),body:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`jj 复用 git 的对象存储但完全替换工作流 UX —— 没有 staging area, 每次保存都是 anonymous commit, branch 像 tag 一样廉价。Google 内部小范围使用, 2025-2026 在 OSS 圈圈了一批早期采用者。短期不会替代 git, 但"git 的 UX 烂"这件事现在有人在认真做 alternative 了。`})})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Jujutsu (jj) takes aim at git's UX`}),body:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`jj reuses git's object store while completely replacing the workflow UX — no staging area, every save is an anonymous commit, branches are as cheap as tags. Used internally at Google in pockets; through 2025–2026 it picked up early adopters in OSS. It will not replace git short-term, but "git's UX is bad" finally has serious competition.`})})}},{tag:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`AI`}),zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`AI agent 重塑 commit cadence`}),body:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`Claude Code / Cursor / Devin 等 agent 自动提交把 "什么算一个 commit" 重新打开。本仓库的现实经验:agent 每完成一个独立小步就 commit, conventional-commit 前缀 (`,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`feat / fix / refactor / docs`}),`) 让历史可机器读。"先 rebase 再 push" 在多 agent 并行下是必修, `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`git bisect`}),` 配合 agent 跑测试脚本变得极其强大。`]})})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`AI agents reshape commit cadence`}),body:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`Auto-commit by Claude Code / Cursor / Devin re-opens "what counts as a commit." This repo's practical experience: an agent commits per small independent step; conventional-commit prefixes (`,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`feat / fix / refactor / docs`}),`) keep history machine-readable. "Rebase before push" is mandatory under parallel agents, and `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`git bisect`}),` driven by an agent test script becomes extremely powerful.`]})})}},{tag:`SCALE`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`百万文件 monorepo 不再特别`}),body:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`partial clone + sparse-index + bundle URI + commit-graph 在 2.46 后全部 stock git 可用。Windows 源码 / Chromium / Android 用 git 同款命令活, 不需要 Microsoft scalar、不需要 git-lfs 特别配置。2026 起 "monorepo 选什么 VCS" 这个问题答案就一个:git。`})})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Mega-monorepos are no longer special`}),body:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`Partial clone + sparse-index + bundle URI + commit-graph are all stock-git from 2.46. Windows source / Chromium / Android live on the same commands the rest of us use — no Microsoft scalar wrapper, no special git-lfs setup. As of 2026 "what VCS for a monorepo" has one answer: git.`})})}},{tag:`RUST`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Rust 模块进 mainline`}),body:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`2.52 起 git mainline 开始接受 Rust 写的 module (reftable backend 第一个)。maintainer 公开承诺"未来 git 会有更多 Rust", 每个 release 加一点。这不是"重写 git", 是"在不破 ABI 的前提下让某些边界 (parser / 编码 / IO 密集) 走 Rust"。`})})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Rust modules enter mainline`}),body:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`Since 2.52 git mainline accepts Rust-authored modules (reftable backend was first). The maintainer publicly committed to "more Rust in future git," shipping incrementally. This isn't "rewrite git" — it's "where it doesn't break ABI (parsers / encoding / IO-heavy paths) move to Rust."`})})}}],cuberoot:{zh:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`本仓库 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`RuiminYan/cuberoot.me`}),` 是一棵 git 树, 既托管 24 个工具页的源代码 (`,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`core/packages/client`}),`), 也托管 Hono 服务端 (`,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`core/packages/server`}),`)、stats build 管道 (`,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`core/packages/stats-build`}),`)、nginx vhost (`,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`ops/nginx/`}),`)、deploy workflow (`,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`.github/workflows/`}),`)。所有跟站点相关的东西 (除 WP blog 外) 都进 git, "改了什么 / 谁改的 / 何时改" 在 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`git log`}),` 里数学上可验证。`]}),(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`分支策略实战:`,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`main`}),` 是 deploy 触发分支, 大部分 PR 走 squash-merge 进 main 保线性历史。Feature 分支 (`,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`sq1/per-piece-transform`}),`、`,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`recon/cache-fix`}),` 等) 在内部用 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`rebase --autostash`}),` 保持跟 main 同步, 避免恶心的 merge commit。Push 之前固定 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`git pull --rebase --autostash origin main`}),`, 是约定不是建议 — 多 AI 并行时这一步漏了立刻冲突。`]}),(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`GitHub Actions 用 path filter 触发对应 deploy:`,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`core/**`}),` 改动跑 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`deploy_core`}),` (build SPA + rsync 到 nginx root + 镜像 GH Pages), `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`ops/nginx/**`}),` 改动跑 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`deploy_nginx`}),` (scp + `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`nginx -t`}),` + reload + 失败 .bak 回滚), `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`stats/**`}),` 改动跑 stats 重 build pipeline。一个 path filter 已知坑:push 文件数 `,`>`,` 300 时 filter 偶尔静默失效, 需要手动 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`gh workflow run deploy_core.yml`}),` 兜底。`]}),(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`多 AI 并行规范:每个 agent 干完一段先 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`git status`}),` 扫别人改了啥, 只 add 自己改的文件 (不用 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`git add -A`}),`), commit 完立刻推。`,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`git log`}),` / `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`git blame`}),` 是权威 — memory 系统刻意不存 git-derivable 信息, 因为 git 自己已经存了。pre-push hook 跑 typecheck 一次 (12s), 失败拒推, 防 CI 红。Worktree 用得越来越多 — 同时改两个 feature 时, 一个 worktree 一个 agent 互不踩。`]})]}),en:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`The repo `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`RuiminYan/cuberoot.me`}),` is a single git tree hosting 24 tool pages' source (`,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`core/packages/client`}),`), the Hono server (`,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`core/packages/server`}),`), the stats build pipeline (`,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`core/packages/stats-build`}),`), the nginx vhost (`,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`ops/nginx/`}),`), and deploy workflows (`,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`.github/workflows/`}),`). Everything site-related except the WP blog lives in git — "what changed, by whom, when" is mathematically verifiable through `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`git log`}),`.`]}),(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`Branching strategy in practice: `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`main`}),` is the deploy-trigger branch; most PRs squash-merge into main to keep history linear. Feature branches (`,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`sq1/per-piece-transform`}),`, `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`recon/cache-fix`}),`, etc.) use `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`rebase --autostash`}),` to stay synced with main and avoid noisy merge commits. `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`git pull --rebase --autostash origin main`}),` before every push is a convention, not a suggestion — skipping it under parallel-AI work guarantees conflicts.`]}),(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`GitHub Actions trigger deploys via path filters: `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`core/**`}),` kicks off `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`deploy_core`}),` (build SPA + rsync to nginx root + mirror to GH Pages); `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`ops/nginx/**`}),` kicks off `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`deploy_nginx`}),` (scp + `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`nginx -t`}),` + reload + .bak rollback on failure); `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`stats/**`}),` kicks off the stats rebuild pipeline. One known path-filter pitfall: pushes with more than 300 files occasionally bypass the filter silently — fallback is a manual `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`gh workflow run deploy_core.yml`}),`.`]}),(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`Multi-AI workflow rules: every agent runs `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`git status`}),` first to scan for others' changes, stages only its own files (never `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`git add -A`}),`), and pushes immediately after committing. `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`git log`}),` / `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`git blame`}),` are authoritative — the memory system intentionally doesn't store git-derivable info because git already has it. A pre-push hook runs typecheck once (~12s) and refuses bad pushes to prevent red CI. Worktrees are used more and more — two features, two worktrees, two agents, no stepping on each other.`]})]})},links:[{label:`git-scm.com`,href:`https://git-scm.com`},{label:`GitHub · git/git`,href:`https://github.com/git/git`},{label:`Pro Git book`,href:`https://git-scm.com/book/en/v2`},{label:`Git 2.54 release notes`,href:`https://github.com/git/git/blob/master/Documentation/RelNotes/2.54.0.txt`},{label:`Jujutsu (jj)`,href:`https://github.com/jj-vcs/jj`}]},{slug:`claude`,name:`Claude`,version:`Opus 4.7`,since:`2023-03`,group:`dev`,accent:`#D97757`,bright:`#E89578`,glyph:`✦`,floats:[`messages`,`system`,`tools`,`thinking`,`vision`,`cache_control`,`tool_use`,`tool_result`,`1M ctx`,`stop_reason`,`usage`,`stream`],zh:{tagline:`Anthropic 的对话/工具/代码 LLM`,role:`cuberoot.me 几乎每一行新代码的合写者。Opus 4.7 是每日驾驶, 1M 上下文整仓库能塞进一次会话。`,heroSub:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`Anthropic 2021 年在旧金山由 Dario / Daniela Amodei 和一群前 OpenAI 研究者创立, 主线是 AI 安全研究。Claude 这一系 LLM 2023 年 3 月开放, 三年后 Opus 4.7 把上下文窗口推到 `,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`1M token`}),`, SWE-bench 全部时段领先, 是`,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`代码 + 长上下文 + 工具使用`}),` 这三条线同时占第一名的模型。`]}),whatDesc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`Claude 是一个 `,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`LLM 家族`}),`, 不是产品。家族里同代有 Haiku (小快便宜) / Sonnet (中) / Opus (大), 通过同一个 messages API 调用。和 GPT 系不同的地方在 `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`Constitutional AI`}),` 训练方法、显式的 thinking 模式、原生 tool use schema 三件事。`]}),historyDesc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`2023 春的 Claude 1 / Instant 是带原型味的对话模型;Claude 2 (2023-07) 一口气把上下文做到 100K, 那时业界还普遍在 8K-32K;Claude 3 家族 (2024-03) 在 MMLU 短暂登顶;3.5 Sonnet (2024-06) 把代码基线抬到现在的高度。Claude 4 (2025-05) 之后是真正的 agent 模型, 直到 2026-04 Opus 4.7 把窗口拉到 1M。`}),conceptsTitle:`messages + tools + thinking`,conceptsDesc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`API 表面其实就 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`messages.create`}),` 一个端点。复杂度全在参数:system prompt、messages 数组 (含 tool_use / tool_result block)、tools schema、thinking、cache_control、stream。理解这一组 primitive 就理解了 Claude 的全部能力。`]}),whyDesc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`2026 年模型选择多了, 但写代码这条线 Claude 还是第一档。原因不止是 SWE-bench 分数: `,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`thinking 模式`}),`、`,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`1M 上下文`}),`、`,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`tool use 原生 schema`}),`、`,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`prompt caching`}),` 四件事配合起来对长任务的可用性甩开了对手。`]}),adoptersTitle:`谁在用`,adoptersDesc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`Cursor 默认走 Claude, Cline / Roo Code / Aider 这一代 agent 工具大多以 Claude 为主力。Vercel AI SDK 出 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`@ai-sdk/anthropic`}),` 一等公民, Notion / Slack / Quora Poe / DuckDuckGo AI Chat 后端都接了 Claude。`]}),cuberootDesc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`本站 95%+ 的代码是和 Claude 协作写出来的。Opus 4.7 是日常 driver, Sonnet 4.6 跑批量小活。1M 上下文让一次会话能装下 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`packages/client`}),` 整个包做整体重构, 不用再切片粘贴。`]}),outlookTitle:`当下与前景`,outlookDesc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`Claude 接下来一年的关键词是 `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`agent`}),`: tool use schema 收敛、长 horizon 任务的 thinking 预算自动化、computer use beta 转正、prompt cache 跨会话化。Anthropic 的成本曲线决定了它对个人开发者会不会持续可负担。`]})},en:{tagline:`Anthropic's chat / tool-use / coding LLM`,role:`Co-author of nearly every new line of code on cuberoot.me. Opus 4.7 is the daily driver — the whole repo fits in one conversation at 1M context.`,heroSub:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`Anthropic was founded in San Francisco in 2021 by Dario and Daniela Amodei with a group of ex-OpenAI researchers; the throughline is AI safety research. The Claude LLM family opened in March 2023; three years later Opus 4.7 pushes context to `,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`1M tokens`}),`, leads SWE-bench across all categories, and is the model holding first place on `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`coding + long context + tool use`}),` simultaneously.`]}),whatDesc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`Claude is a `,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`family of LLMs`}),`, not a product. Each generation ships Haiku (small / fast / cheap), Sonnet (mid), Opus (large), all behind one messages API. What distinguishes it from GPT: the `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`Constitutional AI`}),` training method, an explicit thinking mode, and a native tool-use schema.`]}),historyDesc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Claude 1 / Instant in spring 2023 had prototype energy; Claude 2 (2023-07) shipped a 100K context window when 8K-32K was the industry norm; the Claude 3 family (2024-03) briefly topped MMLU; 3.5 Sonnet (2024-06) set the coding baseline still in use. Claude 4 (2025-05) was the first proper agent model, and in 2026-04 Opus 4.7 stretched the window to 1M.`}),conceptsTitle:`messages + tools + thinking`,conceptsDesc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`The API surface is essentially one endpoint, `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`messages.create`}),`. Complexity is in the parameters: system prompt, the messages array (carrying tool_use / tool_result blocks), tools schema, thinking, cache_control, stream. Understanding that primitive set is understanding Claude.`]}),whyDesc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`2026 has more model choices than ever, but for code Claude is still in a class of its own. It's not just SWE-bench: `,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`thinking mode`}),`, `,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`1M context`}),`, `,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`native tool-use schema`}),`, and `,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`prompt caching`}),` together make long tasks usable in ways competitors don't yet match.`]}),adoptersTitle:`Who uses it`,adoptersDesc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`Cursor defaults to Claude; the agent-tool generation — Cline, Roo Code, Aider — overwhelmingly picks Claude as the workhorse. Vercel AI SDK ships `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`@ai-sdk/anthropic`}),` as a first-class adapter; Notion, Slack, Quora Poe, and DuckDuckGo AI Chat all wire Claude into their backends.`]}),cuberootDesc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`95%+ of this codebase was written with Claude as collaborator. Opus 4.7 is the daily driver; Sonnet 4.6 handles cheaper grunt work. The 1M window lets one session hold the entire `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`packages/client`}),` for a holistic refactor — no more slice-and-paste.`]}),outlookTitle:`Now and next`,outlookDesc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`The next year's keyword is `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`agent`}),`: tool-use schemas converging, automated thinking budgets for long-horizon tasks, computer-use graduating from beta, and prompt cache reaching across sessions. Anthropic's cost curve will decide whether individual devs can keep affording it.`]})},heroStats:[{num:`1`,unit:`M`,zh:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`上下文窗口 `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`Opus 4.7 · 2026-04`})]}),en:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`context window `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`Opus 4.7 · 2026-04`})]})},{num:`Opus 4.7`,zh:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`当前旗舰 `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`claude-opus-4-7`})]}),en:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`current flagship `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`claude-opus-4-7`})]})},{num:`#1`,zh:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`SWE-bench Verified `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`2026-05`})]}),en:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`SWE-bench Verified `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`2026-05`})]})},{num:`95`,unit:`%+`,zh:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`本仓库 LoC 协作产出 `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`cuberoot.me`})]}),en:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`of LoC in this repo co-authored `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`cuberoot.me`})]})}],intro:{zh:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`Anthropic 2021 年在旧金山由 Dario 和 Daniela Amodei 牵头, 带着一群从 OpenAI 出来的研究者成立, 早期资金来自 Google 和 Spark Capital, 后来 Amazon 注资约 40 亿美元。公司主线是 `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`AI 安全研究`}),` —— Constitutional AI 这套方法的目标是让模型可以"自我批评"地拒绝不安全输出, 而不是靠人工每条标注。Claude 这个名字致敬 Claude Shannon。`]}),(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`2023 年 3 月 Claude 1 + Claude Instant 私测开放, 那年夏天的 Claude 2 一口气把上下文做到 100K, 在 GPT-4 还停留在 8K / 32K 的时代直接拉了一个数量级。2024 年 3 月的 Claude 3 家族 (Haiku / Sonnet / Opus) 第一次在 MMLU 短暂超过 GPT-4, 同年 6 月 3.5 Sonnet + Artifacts 把代码生成的基线再抬一档。`}),(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`真正的 agent 时代是 2025-05 的 Claude 4 —— 那一版开始 tool use schema 稳定下来, 多步任务的 reliability 终于可用。之后 4.1 / 4.5 / 4.6 一路把 agent loop 中的失败模式磨平, 2026-04 Opus 4.7 把上下文窗口推到 1M (从此前的 200K 上去五倍), 同时把 SWE-bench Verified 守住第一。这是当前每天写本仓库代码的那个模型。`})]}),en:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`Anthropic was founded in San Francisco in 2021 by Dario and Daniela Amodei together with a group of ex-OpenAI researchers, with early funding from Google and Spark Capital and later ~$4B from Amazon. The throughline is `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`AI safety research`}),` — Constitutional AI lets a model self-critique refusals rather than relying on per-example human labels. The name nods to Claude Shannon.`]}),(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`Claude 1 + Claude Instant opened in private beta in March 2023; that summer's Claude 2 shipped a 100K context window — an order of magnitude over GPT-4's then-8K / 32K. The Claude 3 family (Haiku / Sonnet / Opus) in March 2024 briefly topped MMLU above GPT-4; June 2024's 3.5 Sonnet plus Artifacts raised the code-generation baseline a level higher.`}),(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`The proper agent era began with Claude 4 in May 2025: the tool-use schema stabilized, and multi-step reliability finally became usable. 4.1 / 4.5 / 4.6 ground down failure modes in the agent loop; in 2026-04 Opus 4.7 took the context window to 1M (5× the prior 200K) while holding first place on SWE-bench Verified. That is the model writing code in this repo today.`})]})},history:[{year:`2021`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Anthropic 成立`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Dario / Daniela Amodei 带一批前 OpenAI 研究者在旧金山立项。早期方向:Constitutional AI, 用模型自批评代替每例人工标注。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Anthropic founded`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Dario and Daniela Amodei with a group of ex-OpenAI researchers set up shop in San Francisco. Early thesis: Constitutional AI — model self-critique in place of per-example human labels.`})}},{year:`2023·03`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Claude 1 + Instant`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`第一代 Claude 私测放开, Instant 主打便宜快, Claude 1 主打对齐质量。那年 LLM 圈刚被 GPT-4 震完, Claude 是少数能跟它隔空对话的。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Claude 1 + Instant`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`The first generation opens in private beta. Instant focuses on cheap / fast, Claude 1 on alignment quality. In a year still ringing from GPT-4's release, Claude is one of the few peers in the conversation.`})}},{year:`2023·07`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Claude 2 — 100K context`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`一口气把上下文窗口做到 100K token, 业界普遍还停在 8K-32K。整本书塞进 prompt 第一次变得日常, RAG 设计因此被重画。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Claude 2 — 100K context`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`The context window jumps to 100K tokens while the industry still sits at 8K-32K. "Stuff the whole book into the prompt" becomes routine; RAG architectures get redrawn.`})}},{year:`2024·03`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Claude 3 (Haiku / Sonnet / Opus)`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`第一次出现三档同代家族。Opus 在 MMLU 短暂登顶 GPT-4, Sonnet 性价比第一, Haiku 是当时最快的能力级模型。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Claude 3 (Haiku / Sonnet / Opus)`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`The first tri-tier family in one generation. Opus briefly tops MMLU over GPT-4, Sonnet leads on price/perf, Haiku is the fastest capable model at the time.`})}},{year:`2024·06`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`3.5 Sonnet + Artifacts`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`代码生成基线抬一档, Artifacts 让对话产出的 React / HTML 直接侧栏渲染。这一版是大部分人第一次觉得 LLM "真能写代码"。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`3.5 Sonnet + Artifacts`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Coding baseline takes another step up; Artifacts renders chat-generated React / HTML in a side pane. This release is when most users first felt LLMs could "actually code."`})}},{year:`2024·10`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`3.5 Sonnet (new) + computer use`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`同版本号下迭代权重, 加 computer use beta —— 模型直接读屏幕 / 控制鼠标键盘。这是 agent 路线第一次原生集成进 API。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`3.5 Sonnet (new) + computer use`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Same version number, refreshed weights; computer use beta lets the model read the screen and control mouse / keyboard. First native integration of the agent path into the API.`})}},{year:`2025·02`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`3.7 Sonnet — thinking 模式`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`显式 thinking 参数:让模型把推理链放到一个独立 block, 用户可选 budget。"花更多 token 想得更深" 第一次变成一个 API 旋钮。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`3.7 Sonnet — thinking mode`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`An explicit thinking parameter; the model puts its reasoning chain into a dedicated block with a user-set budget. "Spend more tokens to think harder" becomes a literal API knob.`})}},{year:`2025·05`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Claude 4 家族`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Opus 4 / Sonnet 4。代码与 agent 能力大跨步, 长 horizon 任务的可靠性第一次跨过"能用"的门槛。同期 Claude Code CLI 上线。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Claude 4 family`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Opus 4 / Sonnet 4. A major leap on coding and agent capability — long-horizon tasks cross the "actually usable" threshold for the first time. Claude Code CLI ships alongside.`})}},{year:`2025·08`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Opus 4.1`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`4.1 强化 agent 与 tool use, 失败模式 (循环、错调、放弃) 普遍降低。模型开始能可靠跑 5 - 10 步的 agent loop。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Opus 4.1`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`4.1 strengthens agent / tool use; common failure modes (loops, wrong calls, premature give-ups) drop. Models can reliably run 5- to 10-step agent loops.`})}},{year:`2025·09`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Sonnet 4.5 / Opus 4.5`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`同代再迭代, 把 prompt caching 推向稳定。5 分钟 TTL 的 cache 让 system prompt + 文档前缀的 cost 降到 1/10。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Sonnet 4.5 / Opus 4.5`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`An in-generation iteration that stabilizes prompt caching. The 5-minute TTL cache drops the cost of a long system prompt + doc prefix by ~10×.`})}},{year:`2025·10`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Sonnet 4.6`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Sonnet 这条线继续推进, 性价比再上一档, 代码任务上和上一代 Opus 接近。日常 grunt work 改用 4.6, 留 Opus 给重活。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Sonnet 4.6`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`The Sonnet line pushes further: price/perf rises another step and matches the previous Opus on coding tasks. Daily grunt work shifts to 4.6 while Opus is reserved for heavy lifting.`})}},{year:`2026·01`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Haiku 4.5 / Opus 4.6`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`扩展上下文与多模态稳定化, 视觉输入质量补齐。这一版让 "便宜小模型 + 长 prompt" 的产品变得现实。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Haiku 4.5 / Opus 4.6`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Extended context and matured multimodality; vision input quality catches up. Makes "cheap small model + long prompt" a real product configuration.`})}},{year:`2026·04`,highlight:!0,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Opus 4.7 — 1M 上下文`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`上下文窗口从 200K 直接拉到 1M token, 五倍。整个中等规模仓库 (包括本仓库) 能塞进单次会话。SWE-bench Verified 同步保持第一。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Opus 4.7 — 1M context`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`The context window goes from 200K to 1M tokens — 5×. An entire mid-size repo (this one included) fits in one conversation. SWE-bench Verified stays at #1.`})}},{year:`2026·05`,highlight:!0,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`当前 — Opus 4.7 daily driver`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`本站当前 default 模型即 claude-opus-4-7。Sonnet 4.6 跑批量小活, Haiku 4.5 跑分类与小工具。这页就是 Opus 4.7 写的。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Now — Opus 4.7 daily driver`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`This site's current default is claude-opus-4-7. Sonnet 4.6 covers batch grunt work, Haiku 4.5 handles classification and small utilities. This very page was written by Opus 4.7.`})}}],concepts:[{tag:`A`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`messages.create 基本调用`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`所有 Claude 调用都收敛到一个端点。最少参数:model + messages + max_tokens。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`messages.create — the basic call`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Every Claude request collapses