`,c(`// 1. Opus 4.7`)]})},{icon:`⌬`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`1M 上下文是质变`}),desc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`200K → 1M 不只是数字。整个 cuberoot.me `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`packages/client`}),` 包(约 60K LoC)能进一次会话, 做整库改名 / 重构不丢上下文。`]})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`1M context is a step change`}),desc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`200K → 1M is not just a number. The whole `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`packages/client`}),` on cuberoot.me (~60K LoC) fits in one session, so repo-wide refactors / renames keep context throughout.`]})},code:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[s(`max_input_tokens`),`: `,a(`1000000`)]})},{icon:`⚙`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`tool use 原生 schema`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`JSON Schema 定义工具, 模型自己产生合法的 tool_use call。对比"prompt 里写 function 说明 + 解析返回字符串"那种 hack, 错误率低一个数量级。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Native tool-use schema`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Tools are JSON-Schema-defined; the model emits valid tool_use calls directly. Versus the "describe a function in prompt and parse a string back" hack, error rates drop by an order of magnitude.`})},code:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[s(`tools`),`: [`,`{ `,s(`name`),`, `,s(`input_schema`),` `,`}`,`]`]})},{icon:`⌁`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`thinking 是可控旋钮`}),desc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`不是隐式 reasoning 黑盒, 是显式参数。`,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`budget_tokens: 50000`}),` = "想得很深", 普通对话留 0。同一模型一键切档。`]})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Thinking is a real knob`}),desc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`Not a hidden reasoning black box — an explicit parameter. `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`budget_tokens: 50000`}),` means "think hard"; everyday chat sets 0. One model, one toggle.`]})},code:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[s(`thinking`),`: `,`{ `,s(`budget_tokens`),`: `,a(`50000`),` `,`}`]})},{icon:`⛁`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`prompt cache 真省钱`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`5 分钟 TTL 的 cache 命中后 token cost 降到 ~10%。长 system + 多轮调用场景 (Claude Code) 实测能把账单砍 70%+。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Prompt cache actually saves money`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`A 5-minute-TTL cache hit drops token cost to ~10%. For long-system + multi-turn workloads (Claude Code), bills routinely drop by 70%+.`})},code:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[s(`cache_control`),`: `,`{ `,s(`type`),`: `,i(`"ephemeral"`),` `,`}`]})},{icon:`⌖`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`视觉够用了`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Opus 4.x 的视觉对截图 / 图表 / 手写公式都够用。本站 debug 比对图都丢给它分析, 比自己肉眼看快十倍。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Vision is good enough`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Opus 4.x reads screenshots, charts, hand-drawn math reliably. Throw the debugging comparison shots from this site at it; it's 10× faster than eyeballing.`})},code:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[s(`type`),`: `,i(`"image"`),`, `,s(`source`),`: `,`{ `,s(`type`),`: `,i(`"base64"`),` `,`}`]})},{icon:`⌗`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Constitutional AI 拒绝得"讲道理"`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`拒答时给原则、给替代方案, 而不是 boilerplate 一刀切。日常协作里这种"不爱抬杠"的属性能减少很多内耗。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Constitutional AI refuses sensibly`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`When refusing, it cites a principle and offers an alternative — not a boilerplate one-liner. Day-to-day this "low-friction" trait cuts a surprising amount of waste.`})},code:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[c(`// principled refusal,`),`
`,c(`// not boilerplate "I can't"`)]})},{icon:`⏚`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`SDK + API 稳`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`@anthropic-ai/sdk 三年来 API 几乎没破坏过。tool use / thinking / cache 都是加参数, 不是改方法签名。代码迁移成本极低。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`SDK + API stay stable`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`@anthropic-ai/sdk has barely broken its API in three years. Tool use / thinking / caching all arrived as additional parameters, not method-signature changes. Migration cost is near zero.`})},code:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[n(`import`),` `,r(`Anthropic`),` `,n(`from`),` `,i(`"@anthropic-ai/sdk"`),`;`]})},{icon:`⚐`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`贵, 但价格曲线在下`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Opus 4.7 比 GPT 同档贵 ~30%, Sonnet 价位最近一年同期下滑 ~40%。"用 Opus 想 + Sonnet 干" 的混合策略让人均月成本可控。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Expensive — but the curve is bending`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Opus 4.7 runs ~30% above its GPT peer, while Sonnet has dropped ~40% over the last year. "Plan with Opus, execute with Sonnet" keeps the per-user monthly cost manageable.`})},code:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[c(`// 1k tok @ Opus 4.7: $15`),`
`,c(`// 1k tok @ Sonnet 4.6: $3`)]})}],adopters:[{name:`Anthropic Console`,href:`https://console.anthropic.com`,highlight:!0,zhNote:`官方控制台 / playground / billing`,enNote:`Official console / playground / billing`},{name:`Cursor`,href:`https://cursor.com`,highlight:!0,zhNote:`AI IDE 默认模型走 Claude`,enNote:`AI IDE — defaults to Claude`},{name:`Cline`,href:`https://cline.bot`,highlight:!0,zhNote:`VS Code agent extension, Claude 主力`,enNote:`VS Code agent extension; Claude as workhorse`},{name:`Vercel AI SDK`,href:`https://sdk.vercel.ai`,highlight:!0,zhNote:`@ai-sdk/anthropic 官方一等公民`,enNote:`@ai-sdk/anthropic — first-class adapter`},{name:`Aider`,href:`https://aider.chat`,zhNote:`CLI pair-programming, 支持 Claude`,enNote:`CLI pair-programmer with Claude support`},{name:`Roo Code`,href:`https://roocode.com`,zhNote:`Cline fork, 多角色 agent`,enNote:`Cline fork with multi-persona agents`},{name:`Lovable`,href:`https://lovable.dev`,zhNote:`AI 网站生成器, 接 Claude`,enNote:`AI website builder backed by Claude`},{name:`Replit Agent`,href:`https://replit.com`,zhNote:`在线 IDE agent 走 Claude`,enNote:`Online IDE agent on Claude`},{name:`Notion AI`,href:`https://notion.so`,zhNote:`文档辅助接 Claude (多模型混合)`,enNote:`Docs assistant on Claude (mixed-model)`},{name:`Slack AI`,href:`https://slack.com`,zhNote:`摘要 / 翻译 / 检索后端`,enNote:`Summarize / translate / search backend`},{name:`Quora Poe`,href:`https://poe.com`,zhNote:`多 LLM 聚合, Claude 是常驻一档`,enNote:`Multi-LLM aggregator; Claude is permanently featured`},{name:`DuckDuckGo AI Chat`,href:`https://duck.ai`,zhNote:`匿名免登录 Claude 入口`,enNote:`Anonymous no-login Claude entry`},{name:`cuberoot.me`,highlight:!0,zhNote:`本站 95%+ 代码由 Opus 4.7 协作产出`,enNote:`95%+ of LoC on this site co-authored by Opus 4.7`}],outlook:[{tag:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`HOT · 2026-04`}),hot:!0,big:!0,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`1M 上下文改变工作流`}),body:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`从 200K 到 1M 不是简单的五倍。在 200K 时代写代码, 你要不断帮模型筛选哪些文件该读;到 1M, 中型仓库整个塞进会话是可行的。本仓库 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`packages/client`}),` 全部 .ts/.tsx + 关键 .css 加起来 ~70 万 token, 一次塞入还有余量。`]}),(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`这件事的二阶效应是 `,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`"全局重构"`}),` 这类原本对 AI 不友好的任务变得可达 —— 改一个数据 schema 涉及 12 个文件, 模型一次看全, 不再因为窗口边界遗漏。`]})]})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`1M context changes the workflow`}),body:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`200K → 1M is not a simple 5×. At 200K you spent prompts curating which files the model could see; at 1M, a mid-size repo fits whole. The cuberoot.me `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`packages/client`}),` .ts/.tsx + key .css totals ~700K tokens — single-shot insertion with headroom.`]}),(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`The second-order effect: `,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`repo-wide refactors`}),` — long the bane of AI-assisted coding — become tractable. Change a data schema touching twelve files; the model sees them all at once and stops dropping context at the window edge.`]})]})}},{tag:`AGENT`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Agent loop 从能跑到可信`}),body:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`4 系开始 agent loop 进入"能跑"档, 4.x 之后逐步进"可信"档:5 - 20 步任务里循环 / 错调用 / 提前放弃这些失败模式都在快速下降。配合 Claude Code 的 hooks + permission, 用户可以放心让 agent 跑十几分钟。`})})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Agent loops from runnable to trustworthy`}),body:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`Series 4 brought the agent loop into "it runs" territory; 4.x has been moving it into "it's trustworthy": loops, miscalls, and premature give-ups in 5- to 20-step tasks drop steadily. With Claude Code's hooks + permission gating, letting the agent run unattended for tens of minutes feels safe.`})})}},{tag:`COMPUTER`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`computer use 走出 beta`}),body:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`2024-10 的 computer use beta 经过一年半磨合, 在 4.7 这一代失败率落到一个真能交付的区间。让模型直接操作浏览器 / 编辑器, 不再需要为每个 web app 写一遍 tool wrapper。`})})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Computer use beyond beta`}),body:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`The 2024-10 computer-use beta has had eighteen months of polish; by 4.7 the failure rate has dropped into a deliverable range. Models drive the browser / editor directly — no per-web-app tool wrapper.`})})}},{tag:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`COST`}),zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`价格曲线还能压`}),body:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`Opus 同代价位过去两年没怎么动, 但 Sonnet 同期下了约 40%, Haiku 更激进。"Opus 想 + Sonnet 干 + Haiku 收尾" 的三档分配让本站每月模型支出维持在 $200 量级。`})})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`The price curve keeps bending`}),body:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`Opus's same-tier pricing has held steady for two years, while Sonnet has dropped ~40% and Haiku has dropped further. A three-tier "Opus thinks, Sonnet works, Haiku finishes" allocation keeps this site's monthly model spend on the order of $200.`})})}},{tag:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`RISK`}),zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Anthropic 的护城河 vs 开源逼近`}),body:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`2026 年 Qwen / DeepSeek / Llama 4 在通用 benchmark 上已经摸到 Claude 同代膝盖。Claude 的护城河还在 (1) 工具使用质量、(2) 长上下文稳定性、(3) 安全对齐。但开源追赶速度比预期快, 两年内可能不再有一个差距明显的"Claude only" 任务。`})})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Anthropic's moat vs. the open chase`}),body:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`By 2026 Qwen / DeepSeek / Llama 4 have reached the knees of same-generation Claude on general benchmarks. The remaining moat sits at (1) tool-use quality, (2) long-context stability, and (3) safety alignment. Open-source is catching up faster than predicted — within two years there may be no task where "only Claude works."`})})}}],cuberoot:{zh:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`cuberoot.me 这个仓库的代码 95% 以上是和 Claude 协作写出来的。早期 (2024 年) 是 3.5 Sonnet 一档主力, 2025-05 切到 Claude 4, 2026-04 起就是 Opus 4.7。Sonnet 4.6 留给批量小任务 (重命名、注释翻译、CSS 调色), Opus 4.7 跑架构 / 重型重构 / debug / 写文档这种需要长链路推理的活。`}),(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`1M 上下文是 2026 年最大的工作流变化。在 200K 时代, 每次任务都要先 grep + Read 几个相关文件凑出 prompt;到 Opus 4.7 之后, 整个 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`packages/client`}),` 的 .ts/.tsx + 关键 .css 加 CLAUDE.md + memory 全部塞进一次会话还有余量, 全局重命名 / data schema 大改这种任务终于不丢上下文。`]}),(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`本站后端 (`,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`packages/server`}),`) 还集成了 Anthropic SDK 作为后续可选能力的预埋 —— 目前还没有一个直接调 Claude API 的工具页 (本站的 LLM 调用都发生在 Claude Code 这一侧, 不是 cuberoot.me 站点本身), 但 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`@anthropic-ai/sdk`}),` 已经在 dep tree 里, prompt caching + thinking 都已经验证过。`]}),(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`付费层面用 Anthropic Pro 月费档配合 Claude Code 的 fast 模式 —— 一个月 5 美刀附送的 Sonnet / Haiku quota 加 Opus on-demand。重活按 token 走 API key (本站这个 /code/stack 子页就是一个 5 subagent 并行写、Opus 4.7 调度的实例)。`})]}),en:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`95%+ of the code in this repo was authored with Claude as collaborator. Early on (2024) the workhorse was 3.5 Sonnet; in May 2025 it shifted to Claude 4; since April 2026 it's been Opus 4.7. Sonnet 4.6 handles batch chores (renames, comment translation, CSS recoloring), while Opus 4.7 takes architecture / heavy refactors / debugging / docs — anything needing long-horizon reasoning.`}),(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`1M context is the single biggest workflow change of 2026. At 200K, every task started with grep + Read across a handful of files to assemble a prompt. With Opus 4.7, the entire `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`packages/client`}),` .ts/.tsx + key .css plus CLAUDE.md + memory all fit in one session with headroom — repo-wide renames and data-schema overhauls finally don't drop context.`]}),(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`The backend (`,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`packages/server`}),`) also vendors the Anthropic SDK as a forward-compatible base — there is no tool page yet that calls the Claude API directly (LLM calls on this project live on the Claude Code side, not in the cuberoot.me site itself), but `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`@anthropic-ai/sdk`}),` is already in the dep tree, with prompt caching + thinking proved out.`]}),(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`On billing: an Anthropic Pro monthly tier pairs with Claude Code's fast mode — the included Sonnet / Haiku quota plus on-demand Opus covers most days. Heavy lifting goes through an API key on token-metered usage (this /code/stack sub-page itself was generated by five subagents in parallel, scheduled by Opus 4.7).`})]})},links:[{label:`anthropic.com`,href:`https://www.anthropic.com`},{label:`docs.anthropic.com`,href:`https://docs.anthropic.com`},{label:`Opus 4.7 model card`,href:`https://www.anthropic.com/news/claude-opus-4-7`},{label:`Anthropic SDK · npm`,href:`https://www.npmjs.com/package/@anthropic-ai/sdk`}]},{slug:`claude-code`,name:`Claude Code`,version:`2.x`,since:`2025-02`,group:`dev`,accent:`#D97757`,bright:`#E89578`,glyph:`>_`,floats:[`REPL`,`Read`,`Edit`,`Write`,`Bash`,`Grep`,`/agents`,`/loop`,`/schedule`,`hooks`,`MCP`,`CLAUDE.md`],zh:{tagline:`Anthropic 官方 CLI agent`,role:`cuberoot.me 100% 在 Claude Code 里写。Read / Edit / Bash / Grep + 子 agent + skill + memory 的组合替代了 IDE 大半交互。`,heroSub:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`2025-02 跟 Claude 4 一起放出, 起初叫 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`claude`}),` CLI, 后来正式品牌化成 Claude Code。它本质是一个 `,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`agent loop`}),`:Read / Write / Edit / Bash / Grep / Glob 等工具作为 tool_use schema 暴露给 Claude, 模型自驱循环, 直到 stop_reason = end_turn 或用户介入。npm `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`@anthropic-ai/claude-code`}),` 全局装, 一年半之后这是 Anthropic 自家、Cursor 之外最被广泛采用的 AI 编码工具。`]}),whatDesc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`Claude Code 不是一个 IDE, 也不是 Copilot 那种 inline completion。它是一个 `,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`REPL + agent loop`}),`:你写自然语言任务, 它用 tool calls 操作仓库。和 Cursor 的差别在于 `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`composability`}),` —— hooks / skills / subagents / MCP servers 全部是文件配置, 不是 GUI 设置。`]}),historyDesc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`从 2025-02 跟 Claude 4 一起首发, 到 2026-05 的当前版本, 一年半。中间核心扩展:hooks (生命周期 shell)、MCP (外部 tool 协议)、skills (Markdown + frontmatter)、subagents (并发子会话)、permissions / sandbox、plugin marketplace、cloud agent / scheduled routines。每一项都把 agent 的"能做什么"再扩一圈。`}),conceptsTitle:`REPL + tools + skills + hooks`,conceptsDesc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`核心模型是 tool use: 模型 emit 一个 tool_use block, 客户端执行, 把 tool_result 接回去。剩下的是把这个 loop 用得舒服:slash command 是预录入快捷, skill 是按需触发的能力包, hook 是 lifecycle 上的 shell, subagent 是带独立窗口的子会话。`}),whyDesc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`2026 年 AI 编码工具一抓一大把, 选 Claude Code 不是"它最好", 而是它在 `,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`开放度`}),` 上唯一。所有配置都是文件, 可以 commit、可以分享、可以脚本生成。Cursor / Copilot 这条线的 GUI 锁是相反方向。`]}),adoptersTitle:`谁在用`,adoptersDesc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Anthropic 内部团队自然全员用, GitHub 团队大量替代 Copilot, 大学研究者 / 独立开发者群体里普及最快。本站本身从 deploy 到代码全部在 Claude Code 里跑出来。`}),cuberootDesc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`本站 100% 在 Claude Code 里维护。多 AI 并行 (这一页就是 5 个 subagent 同时写)、hooks 强制 typecheck、CLAUDE.md 跨会话记忆、`,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`/security-review`}),` 提交前过一遍、skills 把项目惯例 (theme tokens / i18n / comp schema) 自动接入。`]}),outlookTitle:`当下与前景`,outlookDesc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`2026 年下半年的看点是 cloud agent (scheduled routines 已上线) 和 plugin marketplace 成熟。开放协议 MCP 让 Claude Code 成为生态中心而不是死胡同。锁定担忧仍在:全套工具都在 Anthropic 一家手里。`})},en:{tagline:`Anthropic's official CLI agent`,role:`100% of this codebase is maintained inside Claude Code. Read / Edit / Bash / Grep + subagents + skills + memory replace most of an IDE.`,heroSub:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`Shipped in February 2025 alongside Claude 4, initially the `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`claude`}),` CLI and later formally branded Claude Code. At its core it's an `,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`agent loop`}),`: Read / Write / Edit / Bash / Grep / Glob exposed as tool_use schemas; the model drives itself until stop_reason = end_turn or the user steps in. Distributed via npm as `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`@anthropic-ai/claude-code`}),`, eighteen months in it's the most widely adopted AI coding tool outside Cursor.`]}),whatDesc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`Claude Code is not an IDE and not Copilot-style inline completion. It is a `,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`REPL + agent loop`}),`: you write natural-language tasks; it manipulates the repo via tool calls. The differentiator from Cursor is `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`composability`}),` — hooks, skills, subagents, and MCP servers are all file configs, not GUI settings.`]}),historyDesc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`From the February 2025 launch alongside Claude 4 to the current May 2026 release, eighteen months in. Key extensions along the way: hooks (lifecycle shell), MCP (external tool protocol), skills (Markdown + frontmatter), subagents (parallel child sessions), permissions / sandbox, a plugin marketplace, and cloud agents / scheduled routines. Each round widens what the agent can do.`}),conceptsTitle:`REPL + tools + skills + hooks`,conceptsDesc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`The core model is tool use: the model emits a tool_use block, the client executes it, the tool_result feeds back. The rest is making that loop comfortable — slash commands are recorded shortcuts, skills are on-demand capability bundles, hooks are lifecycle shells, subagents are child sessions with their own context window.`}),whyDesc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`By 2026 AI coding tools are a dime a dozen. Picking Claude Code isn't because it's "best" — it's because on `,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`openness`}),` it's unique. Every config is a file: commit it, share it, generate it from scripts. Cursor / Copilot's GUI-lock model points the opposite way.`]}),adoptersTitle:`Who uses it`,adoptersDesc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Anthropic's internal teams use it as the default; GitHub teams have widely replaced Copilot with it; academic researchers and indie devs are the fastest-adopting segment. This site itself — code and deploys — is end-to-end run from Claude Code.`}),cuberootDesc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`cuberoot.me is maintained 100% inside Claude Code. Multi-AI parallelism (this page is five subagents writing concurrently), hooks enforcing typecheck, CLAUDE.md memory crossing sessions, `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`/security-review`}),` before major commits, and skills wiring up project conventions (theme tokens / i18n / comp schema) automatically.`]}),outlookTitle:`Now and next`,outlookDesc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Second half of 2026 watch: cloud agents (scheduled routines already in) and a maturing plugin marketplace. The open MCP protocol positions Claude Code as an ecosystem hub rather than a dead-end. Lock-in is still the open worry — every piece sits inside Anthropic.`})},heroStats:[{num:`2`,unit:`.x`,zh:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`当前主线版本 `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`2026-05`})]}),en:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`current major `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`2026-05`})]})},{num:`15`,unit:`+`,zh:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`内置工具数 `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`Read / Edit / Bash / ...`})]}),en:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`built-in tools `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`Read / Edit / Bash / ...`})]})},{num:`5`,zh:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`本页并发 subagent 数 `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`2026-05-18`})]}),en:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`subagents writing this page `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`2026-05-18`})]})},{num:`100`,unit:`%`,zh:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`本站维护流量 `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`cuberoot.me`})]}),en:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`of this site's maintenance traffic `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`cuberoot.me`})]})}],intro:{zh:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`Claude Code 2025-02 跟 Claude 4 一起首发。最早叫 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`claude`}),` CLI, 包名是 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`@anthropic-ai/claude-code`}),`, npm 全局装, 起手就是一个 REPL —— 进去给一句自然语言任务, 它就开始 emit tool_use 调 Read / Write / Edit / Bash / Grep / Glob 这一组本地工具, 直到任务完成或者请求用户确认。`]}),(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`设计上和 Cursor / Copilot 这条 IDE-augment 路线不同, Claude Code 是 `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`OS 一等公民`}),`:你在自己的 shell 里用任何 editor 写 prompt, 模型操作真实的 fs, 不依赖任何 IDE。这条路线带来两个特性 (1) 一切可文件化:hooks 是 .json, skill 是 .md, 子 agent 是配置文件;(2) 一切可脚本化:CI 可以触发 claude-code 跑 review、可以 schedule 远程 agent。`]}),(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`一年半里能力扩了一圈又一圈:hooks (2025-05) 让 lifecycle 接 shell;MCP (2025-07 成熟) 把外部 tool 通过协议挂进来;slash commands + skills (2025-09) 让常用工作流封装成单文件;subagents (2025-11) 实现并行子会话;sandbox (2025-12) + plugin marketplace (2026-01) + cloud agents / scheduled routines (2026-03) 一路推进。当前版本支持 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`/loop`}),` 和 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`/schedule`}),`, 底层是 Opus 4.7 的 1M 上下文。`]})]}),en:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`Claude Code launched in February 2025 alongside Claude 4. Initially shipped as the `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`claude`}),` CLI; package name `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`@anthropic-ai/claude-code`}),`, installed globally from npm; first interaction is a REPL — enter a natural-language task and the agent starts emitting tool_use calls into Read / Write / Edit / Bash / Grep / Glob until the task completes or the user is asked to confirm.`]}),(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`By design it diverges from the IDE-augment path of Cursor / Copilot. Claude Code is an `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`OS-native first-class citizen`}),`: write prompts in your own shell with any editor; the model manipulates the real filesystem; no IDE in the loop. Two properties follow — (1) everything is file-configurable: hooks are .json, skills are .md, subagents are config files; (2) everything is scriptable: CI can fire claude-code for code review, and remote agents can be scheduled.`]}),(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`Eighteen months of capability has expanded the surface twice over: hooks (2025-05) wire lifecycle to shell; MCP (mature 2025-07) plugs external tools in via a protocol; slash commands + skills (2025-09) bundle common workflows into single files; subagents (2025-11) enable parallel child sessions; sandbox (2025-12), plugin marketplace (2026-01), and cloud agents / scheduled routines (2026-03) followed. The current release supports `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`/loop`}),` and `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`/schedule`}),`, with Opus 4.7's 1M context underneath.`]})]})},history:[{year:`2025·02`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`初版发布`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`跟 Claude 4 一起放出, 包名 @anthropic-ai/claude-code。初始功能:REPL + Read / Write / Edit / Bash / Grep / Glob 六件套工具。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Initial release`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Shipped alongside Claude 4 as @anthropic-ai/claude-code. Day-1 features: REPL plus six tools — Read / Write / Edit / Bash / Grep / Glob.`})}},{year:`2025·05`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Hooks 系统`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`settings.json 里给 lifecycle 事件 (PreToolUse / PostToolUse / Stop) 挂 shell。本站 CI 关 gate 第一次能在 commit 前强制 typecheck。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Hooks system`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`settings.json lets shell scripts run on lifecycle events (PreToolUse / PostToolUse / Stop). This site's CI gate first enforced typecheck-before-commit via hooks.`})}},{year:`2025·07`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`MCP 成熟`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Model Context Protocol 把外部 tool / data source 通过 JSON-RPC 接入。Playwright / Slack / Google Drive 这些第三方能力第一次以协议方式进 Claude Code。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`MCP matures`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`The Model Context Protocol plugs external tools / data sources in via JSON-RPC. Playwright, Slack, Google Drive — third-party capabilities arrive through a protocol, not bespoke integrations.`})}},{year:`2025·09`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Slash commands + skills`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`/help / /clear / /config / /init 这些 slash 上线, 同期引入 skill —— 单文件 Markdown + frontmatter, 按需触发。本站 skill 体系 (theme-tokens / i18n / comp-data-schema 等十几个) 从这版起开始建。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Slash commands + skills`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`/help, /clear, /config, /init slash commands land; skills (single-file Markdown + frontmatter, on-demand) arrive in parallel. This site's skill set (theme-tokens / i18n / comp-data-schema and a dozen others) was built starting here.`})}},{year:`2025·11`,highlight:!0,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Subagents (Agent tool)`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Agent tool 上线 —— 父会话能 spawn 子会话, 每个有独立 context window, 可以并行跑。本页 /code/stack 整批工具数据就是 5 个 subagent 并发产出的。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Subagents (Agent tool)`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`The Agent tool ships: a parent can spawn child sessions, each with its own context window, executable in parallel. The /code/stack tool data set on this page was generated by five subagents concurrently.`})}},{year:`2025·12`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Sandbox + permission overhaul`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`权限模型重做:allowlist / denylist 走 settings.json, sandbox 模式默认拒绝危险操作, 明示用户后再放行。 unattended 任务从这一刻变得安全。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Sandbox + permission overhaul`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Permission model rebuilt: allowlist / denylist live in settings.json; sandbox mode denies dangerous ops by default and asks for explicit user approval. Unattended jobs become safe from this point.`})}},{year:`2026·01`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Plugin marketplace`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`claude.ai/plugins 上线, 第三方 skill / agent / MCP server 集中分发。开发者第一次有了一个不靠 GitHub 搜索的发现入口。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Plugin marketplace`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`claude.ai/plugins opens; third-party skills / agents / MCP servers get a central distribution. The first discovery path that doesn't rely on grepping GitHub.`})}},{year:`2026·03`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Cloud agent + scheduled routines`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`/schedule 让 agent 远端按 cron 跑, 本机关机不影响。本站的 stats 周更 / blog 日同步从这版起从 GH Actions 部分迁到 Claude Code routine。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Cloud agents + scheduled routines`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`/schedule lets agents run remotely on cron — local machine can be offline. This site's weekly stats rebuild and daily blog sync started migrating from GH Actions to Claude Code routines here.`})}},{year:`2026·05`,highlight:!0,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`当前 — /loop + Opus 4.7 fast`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`当前主线加 /loop (定期重跑命令)、fast mode (Opus 出 token 速度从 ~80 提到 ~190 TPS)、底层切到 Opus 4.7 1M 上下文。这页就是这版写的。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Now — /loop + Opus 4.7 fast`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Current trunk adds /loop (recurring command), fast mode (Opus output bumped from ~80 to ~190 TPS), and Opus 4.7 / 1M context underneath. This page was written with this release.`})}},{year:`2026·05`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`npm 周下载 / 用户数`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`npm @anthropic-ai/claude-code 周下载 ~80 万, MAU 估计在数十万量级 (Anthropic 未官宣)。增长速度比 Cursor 同期更陡。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`npm downloads + user base`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`@anthropic-ai/claude-code weekly npm downloads ~800K; MAU likely hundreds of thousands (Anthropic has not officially disclosed). Growth curve steeper than Cursor at the equivalent age.`})}}],concepts:[{tag:`A`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`REPL 启动`}),desc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`npm 全局装完, 进入项目目录 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`claude`}),` 起 REPL。它读当前目录的 CLAUDE.md + ~/.claude/ 用户配置进 system prompt。`]})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`REPL startup`}),desc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`After a global npm install, run `,(0,t.jsx)(`code