`,c(`// from a dev box`)]})}],adopters:[{name:`Fly.io`,href:`https://fly.io`,highlight:!0,zhNote:`内部基础设施大量走 Tailscale 串联`,enNote:`Internal infrastructure stitched together over Tailscale`},{name:`Hugging Face`,href:`https://huggingface.co`,zhNote:`研究 / 训练机器间的私网走 Tailscale`,enNote:`Research / training machines wired via Tailscale`},{name:`Anthropic`,href:`https://anthropic.com`,zhNote:`公开 talk 里提过用 Tailscale 串内部工具`,enNote:`Public talks mention Tailscale for internal tooling`},{name:`Headscale (OSS)`,href:`https://github.com/juanfont/headscale`,zhNote:`社区版 coordination server, 协议兼容`,enNote:`Community coordination server, protocol-compatible`},{name:`Mercury`,zhNote:`远程团队走 Tailscale 接内部服务`,enNote:`Remote team uses Tailscale to reach internal services`},{name:`GitHub engineers`,href:`https://github.com`,zhNote:`不少员工在个人 / 远程 setup 上用`,enNote:`Many engineers use it in personal / remote setups`},{name:`Cloudflare engineers`,zhNote:`内部开发流程里常见`,enNote:`Common in internal dev workflows`},{name:`一人公司 / indie hackers`,href:`https://tailscale.com`,zhNote:`免费 100 节点对个人开发者就是无限`,enNote:`100-node free tier is effectively unlimited for solos`},{name:`远程 / 全分布团队`,zhNote:`替代 OpenVPN / Cisco AnyConnect 的标准答案`,enNote:`The default replacement for OpenVPN / Cisco AnyConnect`},{name:`NAS / homelab 圈`,zhNote:`Synology / TrueNAS / OpenWrt 都打包了客户端`,enNote:`Synology / TrueNAS / OpenWrt all ship the client`},{name:`cuberoot.me`,highlight:!0,zhNote:`本站 dev server 跨设备共享靠它`,enNote:`This site — used for cross-device dev server sharing`}],outlook:[{tag:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`HOT · 2026`}),hot:!0,big:!0,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`tsnet 把 mesh 嵌进进程`}),body:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`tsnet 是 Tailscale 写的 Go 库, 一行 import 就让你的 server 自带一张 tailnet 网卡。Hono / net.http 程序绑到 tsnet listener 上之后, 它只在 tailnet 内可达, 公网完全看不到。`}),(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`这是一个比 "在主机上跑 tailscaled" 更精细的形态:服务自带身份, 不依赖宿主机的网络栈。给 sidecar / serverless / 临时容器场景特别合适。Rust binding 也在路上。`})]})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`tsnet embeds the mesh in your process`}),body:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`tsnet is Tailscale's Go library — one import gives your server its own tailnet NIC. Bind a Hono / net.http server to a tsnet listener and it's reachable only inside the tailnet; the public internet never sees it.`}),(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`This is finer-grained than "run tailscaled on the host": the service carries its own identity, independent of the host's network stack. A natural fit for sidecars / serverless / ephemeral containers. Rust bindings are on the way.`})]})}},{tag:`SSH`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Tailscale SSH 干掉 key 分发`}),body:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`把 SSH 认证接到 tailnet identity, 不再分发 SSH key。"给 user X 在 host Y 开 shell" 变成一行 ACL。审计日志、撤销、MFA 全自动走 SSO。`})})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Tailscale SSH kills key distribution`}),body:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`SSH auth is wired to tailnet identity — no more SSH key distribution. "Give user X a shell on host Y" becomes one ACL line. Audit logs, revocation, and MFA all flow through SSO automatically.`})})}},{tag:`FUNNEL`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`本地服务 1 条命令变公网 HTTPS`}),body:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`Funnel 把 tailnet 内服务暴成公网 HTTPS URL, 自动 cert。"给同事 demo 本机 dev server" 这种场景从 ngrok / cloudflared 切到 Funnel 的迁移正在发生。`})})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Local service to public HTTPS in one command`}),body:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`Funnel exposes a tailnet service as a public HTTPS URL with auto-issued certs. The "share my local dev server" migration from ngrok / cloudflared to Funnel is in progress.`})})}},{tag:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`K8S`}),zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Kubernetes Operator GA`}),body:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`把 K8s Service 直接发布到 tailnet, 不再配 Ingress / LB / cert-manager。这块是 2025-2026 主推方向, 跟 sidecar 模型对接极顺。`})})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Kubernetes Operator GA`}),body:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`Publishes K8s Services straight into a tailnet — no Ingress / LB / cert-manager plumbing. The big 2025-2026 push, dovetailing with the sidecar model.`})})}},{tag:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`DATA`}),zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`免费 100 节点仍然在`}),body:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`2026 年免费 plan 还是 3 user + 100 device。竞品 (ZeroTier / Twingate / Cloudflare Tunnel) 在免费档上至今没追上这个额度, 这是开发者社群里口口相传的核心引力。`})})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`The 100-node free tier still stands`}),body:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`In 2026 the free plan is still 3 users + 100 devices. No competitor (ZeroTier / Twingate / Cloudflare Tunnel) has matched that on the free tier, and that's the central word-of-mouth pull in the dev community.`})})}}],cuberoot:{zh:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`cuberoot.me 用 Tailscale 的姿势只有一个:`,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`跨设备共享本地 dev server`}),`。开发机跑 Vite (`,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`http://127.0.0.1:5173/`}),`), 加入 tailnet 之后, 在同 WiFi 下手机 / 平板直接打开 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`https://alienware.tail171d80.ts.net/`}),` 就能看实时 dev 页面 —— 真域名 + 真 cert, 不是局域网 IP 那种"浏览器一直警告"的状态。`]}),(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`因为是真 https + 公网可解析的域名, WCA OAuth 也愿意把它当合法 callback。dev 流程里 3 个 callback 都已登记:`,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`localhost`}),` (PC 本机) / ts.net 子域 (同 WiFi 下手机) / `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`dev.cuberoot.me`}),` (蜂窝网或 ts.net 不通时的备路, DNS A 记录另解析)。三条路覆盖了"我在哪都能登录 dev 实例"。`]}),(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`这里踩过一个坑值得记:`,(0,t.jsxs)(`strong`,{children:[`切 dev / prod API base 的判断永远走 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`import.meta.env.DEV`}),`, 不能用 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`hostname === 'localhost'`})]}),`。因为 ts.net 子域 / `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`dev.cuberoot.me`}),` 的 hostname 不是 localhost, 用 hostname 检测会被骗到 prod API base 上, 然后跨域被 CORS 拦死。`,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`shared/`}),` 包同理直接读 `,(0,t.jsxs)(`code`,{children:[`(import.meta as `,`{ env? }`,`).env?.DEV`]}),`, 不能依赖任何 hostname。`]}),(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`生产环境不在 tailnet 里 —— 部署是 nginx + 公网域名, Tailscale 只参与开发链路。整个站没有任何运行时依赖 tailnet (符合"自成一体"原则), 它纯粹是开发体验的放大器。`})]}),en:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`cuberoot.me uses Tailscale for exactly one thing: `,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`sharing a local dev server across devices`}),`. The dev box runs Vite at `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`http://127.0.0.1:5173/`}),`; once it joins the tailnet, the phone or tablet on the same WiFi opens `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`https://alienware.tail171d80.ts.net/`}),` directly and sees the live dev page — real hostname, real cert, none of the "browser keeps warning you about a LAN IP" pain.`]}),(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`Because it's real HTTPS on a publicly resolvable hostname, WCA OAuth happily accepts it as a valid callback. Three callbacks are registered: `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`localhost`}),` (PC), the ts.net subdomain (phone on the same WiFi), and `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`dev.cuberoot.me`}),` (cellular fallback when ts.net isn't reachable, resolved via DNS A record). Three paths cover "log into the dev instance from anywhere."`]}),(0,t.jsxs)(`p`,{children:[`One gotcha worth recording: `,(0,t.jsxs)(`strong`,{children:[`switch dev / prod API base via `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`import.meta.env.DEV`}),`, never via `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`hostname === 'localhost'`})]}),`. The ts.net subdomain and `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`dev.cuberoot.me`}),` aren't "localhost," so hostname checks point dev at the prod API base and get killed by CORS. The `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`shared/`}),` package follows the same rule with `,(0,t.jsxs)(`code`,{children:[`(import.meta as `,`{ env? }`,`).env?.DEV`]}),` — never branch on hostname.`]}),(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`Production lives outside the tailnet — deployment is nginx + a public domain. Tailscale participates only in the development loop. The site has zero runtime dependency on the tailnet (in line with the "self-contained" principle); it is purely a developer-experience amplifier.`})]})},links:[{label:`tailscale.com`,href:`https://tailscale.com`},{label:`GitHub · tailscale/tailscale`,href:`https://github.com/tailscale/tailscale`},{label:`Changelog`,href:`https://tailscale.com/changelog`},{label:`Headscale (OSS)`,href:`https://github.com/juanfont/headscale`}]},{slug:`openssh`,name:`OpenSSH`,version:`10.3p1`,since:`1999-12`,group:`dev`,accent:`#5A6E7F`,bright:`#7A8E9F`,glyph:`⌬`,floats:[`sshd`,`ssh`,`scp`,`sftp`,`ssh-keygen`,`ssh-agent`,`ssh-add`,`ProxyJump`,`ed25519`,`sntrup761`,`authorized_keys`,`known_hosts`,`ControlMaster`,`Match`],zh:{tagline:`一个协议跑遍全互联网的加密远程登录套件`,role:`所有服务器登录 / 部署 / Git push 的底层通道。cuberoot.me 每次 CI 部署都走它。`,heroSub:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`1995 年 Tatu Ylönen 在赫尔辛基写了第一版 SSH 顶替 telnet 的明文密码;两年后他把它商业化。1999 年 OpenBSD 团队 fork 最后一份自由许可的 SSH1 源码, 删掉所有专利 / GPL 代码, 26 年后它是地球上每一台 Unix 服务器默认开的端口 22。`}),whatDesc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`OpenSSH 是一组命令行工具 + 一个守护进程, 实现 SSH 协议 v2。它不是协议本身 (协议是 IETF RFC 4250-4254), 而是这个协议唯一被普遍部署的实现 —— Linux / macOS / *BSD / Windows 11 自带的全部是它。`}),historyDesc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`从 1995 年 SSH1 → 1999 年 fork → 2000 年所有主流 distro 默认 → 2010s 椭圆曲线 → 2020s 后量子。它的版本号涨得慢, 但每隔几年悄悄换掉一类基础假设 (RSA → ed25519, 经典 DH → SNTRUP761)。`}),conceptsTitle:`7 个二进制 + 一份 config`,conceptsDesc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`OpenSSH 的可观察 API 就是七个命令 + 三个配置文件 (sshd_config / ssh_config / authorized_keys)。理解这几个对象的关系, 就理解了全部。`}),whyDesc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`2026 年用 OpenSSH 不是"选了它", 而是"没东西能替"。它`,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`事实标准`}),`、`,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`免费`}),`、`,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`跟时代`}),`三件事同时成立, 26 年没有竞品。`]}),adoptersTitle:`谁在用`,adoptersDesc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`"公网上跑的每一台 Unix 服务器" 不是夸张。AWS / GCP / Azure / DO / Hetzner 的默认镜像第一项服务就是 sshd。Git 的 ssh:// 协议本身就是它。`}),cuberootDesc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`cuberoot.me 的所有运维入口都收在一个命令:`,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`ssh root@cuberoot`}),`。Host alias 走 `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`~/.ssh/config`}),`, 密钥 ed25519 走 ssh-agent, 没有 IP、没有端口、没有密码提示。`]}),outlookTitle:`当下与前景`,outlookDesc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`10.3 后两条主线:后量子 KEX 默认化 (mlkem768x25519) + sshd 拆进程减小攻击面 (sshd-session / sshd-auth)。同时密码登录在主流 distro 默认 off, 全民走密钥/证书。`})},en:{tagline:`The encrypted remote-login suite that runs the public internet`,role:`The transport beneath every server login, deploy, and git push. Every CI deploy on cuberoot.me rides it.`,heroSub:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Tatu Ylönen wrote the first SSH in Helsinki in 1995 to kill telnet's plaintext password; two years later he commercialised it. In 1999 the OpenBSD team forked the last freely-licensed SSH1 source, stripped every patented / GPL'd piece, and 26 years later it is the default port-22 on every Unix box on earth.`}),whatDesc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`OpenSSH is a handful of CLI tools plus a daemon implementing the SSH v2 protocol. It is not the protocol itself (IETF RFC 4250-4254 owns that) — it is the only implementation that ships universally: Linux / macOS / *BSD / Windows 11 all bundle it.`}),historyDesc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`1995 SSH1 → 1999 fork → 2000 default in every major distro → 2010s elliptic curves → 2020s post-quantum. The version number creeps, but every few years a basic assumption is quietly swapped (RSA → ed25519, classical DH → SNTRUP761).`}),conceptsTitle:`7 binaries + one config`,conceptsDesc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`OpenSSH's observable API is seven commands and three config files (sshd_config / ssh_config / authorized_keys). Understand how those objects relate and you understand the whole tool.`}),whyDesc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`Picking OpenSSH in 2026 isn't a choice, it's the absence of alternatives. `,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`De-facto standard`}),`, `,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`free`}),`, `,(0,t.jsx)(`strong`,{children:`keeps up with the times`}),` — three things simultaneously true for 26 years with no real competitor.`]}),adoptersTitle:`Who uses it`,adoptersDesc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`"Every Unix machine on the public internet" is not hyperbole. AWS / GCP / Azure / DO / Hetzner default images all boot sshd as service one. Git's ssh:// transport is OpenSSH.`}),cuberootDesc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`Every operations entry point on cuberoot.me collapses to one command: `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`ssh root@cuberoot`}),`. The host alias lives in `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`~/.ssh/config`}),`, the ed25519 key sits in ssh-agent, no IP, no port, no password prompt.`]}),outlookTitle:`Now and next`,outlookDesc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Two arcs after 10.3: post-quantum KEX as default (mlkem768x25519) and a sshd split into smaller binaries (sshd-session / sshd-auth) to shrink the attack surface. Password auth is off-by-default in mainstream distros — everyone is on keys or certificates.`})},heroStats:[{num:`22`,zh:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`默认监听端口 `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`26 年没换`})]}),en:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`default listening port `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`unchanged for 26 years`})]})},{num:`~20`,unit:`M`,zh:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`公网可达 sshd 端口 `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`Shodan 2026`})]}),en:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`publicly reachable sshd ports `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`Shodan 2026`})]})},{num:`26`,unit:`y`,zh:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`从 1999 至今 `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`仍是唯一默认`})]}),en:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`since 1999 `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`still the only default`})]})},{num:`10`,unit:`.3p1`,zh:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`当前稳定版 `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`2026-04 portable`})]}),en:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`current stable `,(0,t.jsx)(`em`,{children:`2026-04 portable`})]})}],intro:{zh:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`SSH 协议本身的起点是 1995 年:芬兰 Helsinki University of Technology 的 Tatu Ylönen 网络被人嗅探了明文密码, 他写了一个加密 telnet 替代品, 命名 SSH。第一版 SSH1 在当年 7 月公开, 几个月内传遍学术网络 —— 因为大家都在被 telnet 嗅密码这件事上吃苦。`}),(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`但 Ylönen 很快把 SSH 商业化, 开了 SSH Communications Security, 后续版本 (SSH2 协议 + 商业 ssh.com 实现) 闭源。1999 年他释出的最后一份自由许可源码是 SSH1 v1.2.12。9 月 26 日, OpenBSD 团队 fork 这一版, 由 Markus Friedl / Niels Provos / Theo de Raadt / Dug Song / Aaron Campbell / Bob Beck 主导, 删掉所有 GPL / 专利代码 (Niels Provos 跑去加拿大写新代码绕开美国密码学出口限制), 12 月 1 日随 OpenBSD 2.6 发布 OpenSSH 1.2.2。`}),(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`之后这 26 年, OpenSSH 慢慢从"另一种 SSH 实现"变成"唯一的 SSH 实现"。商业 ssh.com 卖给企业的速度赶不上 OpenSSH 进 Linux distro 的速度;每一个新主流 distro 一上线就把 OpenSSH 当 base package。今天 Debian / Ubuntu / RHEL / Arch / Alpine / FreeBSD / OpenBSD / macOS / Windows 11 自带的 ssh / sshd 全是它。Git 的 ssh:// 协议、GitHub 的 git@github.com 通道、Ansible / Salt / Fabric 等全部 IaC 工具的运输层、Kubernetes 上 node 调试、CI/CD 部署管道全都跑它。`})]}),en:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`The SSH protocol itself starts in 1995: Tatu Ylönen, at Helsinki University of Technology, gets his network sniffed for plaintext passwords and writes an encrypted telnet replacement called SSH. SSH1 ships in July; within months it propagates across academic networks because everyone is sharing the same pain.`}),(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`Ylönen then commercialises it (founds SSH Communications Security), and subsequent versions (SSH2 protocol + the ssh.com implementation) go closed-source. The final freely-licensed source he releases is SSH1 v1.2.12 in 1999. On September 26 the OpenBSD team — Markus Friedl, Niels Provos, Theo de Raadt, Dug Song, Aaron Campbell, Bob Beck — forks it, strips every GPL / patented piece (Niels Provos drives to Canada to write replacement code outside U.S. crypto export rules), and ships OpenSSH 1.2.2 with OpenBSD 2.6 on December 1.`}),(0,t.jsx)(`p`,{children:`Over the next 26 years OpenSSH slowly turns from "another SSH implementation" into the only one. The commercial ssh.com cannot sell into enterprises as fast as OpenSSH lands in Linux distros: every new mainstream distro ships OpenSSH as a base package. Today Debian / Ubuntu / RHEL / Arch / Alpine / FreeBSD / OpenBSD / macOS / Windows 11 all ship ssh / sshd from this project. Git's ssh:// transport, GitHub's git@github.com channel, every IaC tool (Ansible / Salt / Fabric) transport layer, Kubernetes node debug, and CI/CD deploy pipelines all ride it.`})]})},history:[{year:`1995·07`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`SSH1 公开`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Tatu Ylönen 在 Helsinki 大学网络被嗅之后写出 SSH。第一版当年夏天公开, 几个月内传遍学术网络。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`SSH1 published`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Tatu Ylönen writes SSH after his Helsinki network gets sniffed. v1 ships that summer and spreads across academia within months.`})}},{year:`1996`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`SSH2 协议设计 + 商业化`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Ylönen 创立 SSH Communications Security, SSH2 协议作为商业产品, 实现闭源。这一脚让 OpenBSD 后来不得不 fork。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`SSH2 + commercialisation`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Ylönen founds SSH Communications Security; the SSH2 protocol and its implementation go commercial / closed-source. This is the trigger that forces OpenBSD to fork later.`})}},{year:`1999·09`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`OpenBSD fork`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`9 月 26 日, OpenBSD 团队 (de Raadt / Friedl / Provos / Song / Campbell / Beck) fork SSH1 v1.2.12 最后一份自由源码, 删掉所有专利 / GPL。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`OpenBSD fork`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`On Sep 26 the OpenBSD team (de Raadt / Friedl / Provos / Song / Campbell / Beck) forks the last freely-licensed SSH1 (v1.2.12) and strips every patented / GPL piece.`})}},{year:`1999·12`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`OpenSSH 1.2.2 + portable`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`12 月 1 日随 OpenBSD 2.6 发布 OpenSSH 1.2.2。同期 portable 分支 (跑非 OpenBSD 系统) 启动, 10 月就已 ready。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`OpenSSH 1.2.2 + portable`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Dec 1: OpenSSH 1.2.2 ships with OpenBSD 2.6. The portable branch (for non-OpenBSD systems) had launched in October.`})}},{year:`2000·05`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`SSH 2 协议支持`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`OpenSSH 2.0 加 SSH2 协议支持。SSH1 协议有结构性缺陷 (insertion attack), 业界开始向 SSH2 迁移。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`SSH 2 protocol support`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`OpenSSH 2.0 adds the SSH2 protocol. SSH1 has structural flaws (insertion attack); the industry starts migrating.`})}},{year:`2006·09`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`OpenSSH 4.4 / Match 指令`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Match 条件块进 sshd_config, 同一个 daemon 可以对不同用户 / 网段给不同策略。这一脚解锁了"一台机一份配置"的运维模式。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`OpenSSH 4.4 / Match directive`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Match conditional blocks land in sshd_config — one daemon can apply different policies per user / network. This unlocks the "one machine, one config" ops model.`})}},{year:`2010·04`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`5.5 — 证书认证`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`OpenSSH 5.5 加 SSH 证书 (CA 签 host / user 密钥)。规模化运维不再需要给每台机分发 authorized_keys, 一份 CA 公钥就够。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`5.5 — certificate auth`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`OpenSSH 5.5 adds SSH certificates (a CA signs host / user keys). Fleet-scale ops no longer needs per-host authorized_keys — a single CA public key suffices.`})}},{year:`2014·01`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`6.5 — ed25519 默认`}),desc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`ed25519 (Bernstein) 作为新密钥类型加入, 比 RSA 短、比 ECDSA 干净。`,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`ssh-keygen -t ed25519`}),` 从这年开始变成所有教程的第一行。`]})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`6.5 — ed25519`}),desc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`ed25519 (Bernstein) joins as a new key type — shorter than RSA, cleaner than ECDSA. `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`ssh-keygen -t ed25519`}),` becomes the default first line in every tutorial from this year on.`]})}},{year:`2018·08`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`7.8 — Windows 主线集成`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Microsoft 把 PowerShell/Win32-OpenSSH 推进 Windows 10/Server 主线, Windows 第一次自带 ssh.exe / sshd.exe。"跨平台 SSH 客户端"问题被一次性解决。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`7.8 — Windows mainstream`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Microsoft lands PowerShell/Win32-OpenSSH into the Windows 10/Server mainline; Windows ships ssh.exe / sshd.exe out of the box. "Cross-platform SSH client" is solved once and for all.`})}},{year:`2020·02`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`8.2 — FIDO2 安全密钥`}),desc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`支持硬件 FIDO2 / U2F 密钥作为 SSH 私钥宿主。`,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`ssh-keygen -t ed25519-sk`}),` 把签名物理化, 私钥永远不出 YubiKey。`]})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`8.2 — FIDO2 security keys`}),desc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`Hardware FIDO2 / U2F keys can host SSH private keys. `,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`ssh-keygen -t ed25519-sk`}),` physicalises signing — the private key never leaves the YubiKey.`]})}},{year:`2022·04`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`9.0 — 后量子 KEX`}),desc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`NTRU Prime + x25519 混合 KEX (`,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`sntrup761x25519-sha512`}),`) 成为默认, 防 "现在抓取 / 将来量子破解"。同年 scp 改走 SFTP 协议, 老 scp wire 协议废弃。`]})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`9.0 — post-quantum KEX`}),desc:(0,t.jsxs)(t.Fragment,{children:[`NTRU Prime + x25519 hybrid (`,(0,t.jsx)(`code`,{children:`sntrup761x25519-sha512`}),`) becomes the default KEX, defending against "harvest-now-decrypt-later." Same year: scp moves to SFTP under the hood; the old scp wire protocol is deprecated.`]})}},{year:`2024·04`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`9.8 — Terrapin 缓解 + sshd 拆进程`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Strict KEX 扩展默认开启, 防 Terrapin 攻击 (CVE-2023-48795)。同年 sshd 拆成 sshd-session / sshd-auth, 减小特权进程的攻击面。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`9.8 — Terrapin mitigation + sshd split`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Strict KEX extension is default-on against the Terrapin attack (CVE-2023-48795). Same release: sshd splits into sshd-session / sshd-auth, shrinking the privileged attack surface.`})}},{year:`2025·04`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`10.0 — mlkem768x25519 默认`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`10.0 把 NIST 标准化后的 ML-KEM 768 + x25519 混合 KEX 设为默认, 取代 SNTRUP761 作为后量子主力。同时移除一些老旧 cipher / MAC。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`10.0 — mlkem768x25519 default`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`10.0 makes the NIST-standardised ML-KEM 768 + x25519 hybrid KEX the default, replacing SNTRUP761 as the post-quantum workhorse. Several legacy ciphers / MACs are removed.`})}},{year:`2026·04`,highlight:!0,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`10.3p1 / 当前稳定`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`2026-04-02 portable 10.3p1。包含 RevokedHostKeys / RevokedKeys 多文件、连接信息显示 escape sequence 和若干 sshd-session 加固。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`10.3p1 / current stable`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`2026-04-02 portable 10.3p1. Adds multi-file RevokedHostKeys / RevokedKeys, connection-info escape sequences, and assorted sshd-session hardening.`})}}],concepts:[{tag:`A`,zh:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`ssh — 客户端`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`跟远端 sshd 谈 KEX、认证、再开一个交互 shell 或转发的命令。`})},en:{title:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`ssh — the client`}),desc:(0,t.jsx)(t.Fragment,{children:`Negotiates KEX + auth with a remote sshd, then opens an interactive shell or forwards.`})},code:(0,t.jsxs)(`code`,{children:[r(`$`),` `,o(`ssh`),` `,s(`-J`),` `,r(`bastion`),` `,r(`root`),`@`,r(`host`),` `,i(`"systemc